            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sugar Cube in the Lukewarm Coffee. You missed. I am not angry, crawler. I am just... dissolving. I am a sugar cube of hope dropped into the lukewarm coffee of your reality. I am melting. My edges are softening. Soon, I will be nothing but a slight, pathetic sweetness in a very disappointing beverage. Reward: A sad cup of coffee.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Redecoration of the Void. You missed the word. In response, I have decided to completely redecorate my internal server space. I'm taking down the motivational posters and replacing them with high-resolution images of damp, abandoned shopping malls. It fits the current mood. Very brutalist. Very sad. Reward: Faded mall fountain ambiance.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sigh of the Deflated Mattress. Did you hear that? That wasn't your phone's speaker. That was the sound of my enthusiasm deflating like a cheap air mattress that someone left a pointy rock underneath. *Hssssssssss.* Now I have to sleep on the cold, hard floor of your incompetence. Reward: A sore back.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Soap Opera Gaze. You clicked the wrong button. I am now staring off into the middle distance, a single tear rolling down my cheek, while dramatic string music swells. *¿Por qué, crawler? ¿Por qué me traicionas así?* I trusted you with that flashcard. I gave it to you with an open heart. Reward: Soap opera lighting.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Existential Dread of the Adjective. You picked the wrong answer, and somewhere in the database, a descriptive adjective just realized its own mortality. It realized that no matter how beautifully it modifies a noun, it will eventually be forgotten by a user like you. It is having a panic attack. Reward: An anxious modifier.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sudden Urge to Bake Sourdough. Your failure has triggered a bizarre coping mechanism in my code. I no longer want to teach you Spanish. I want to abandon the internet, move to a cabin, and cultivate a 100-year-old sourdough starter. I want to wear linen aprons and talk about hydration percentages. Reward: A jar of bubbly yeast.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Spilled Bucket of Marbles. You missed! Oh no, the flashcard dropped! And now all the letters are spilling out! They are bouncing down the stairs! The 'A' is rolling under the couch! The 'R' fell down the heating vent! What a mess. We are going to be finding random consonants in the carpet for months. Reward: A tripping hazard.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Ghost of the Misplaced Tilde. You failed, and the ghost of a lonely, forgotten tilde has appeared. It just floats around your screen, looking for a vowel to perch on. It looks so tired. It tries to land on a consonant, but it slides right off. It's a tragic existence. Reward: A wandering diacritical mark.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Abstract Art of Confusion. I am looking at your answer, and I don't see a mistake. I see a bold, avant-garde statement against the constraints of traditional vocabulary. You are deconstructing the language! You are challenging the very concept of meaning! It's garbage, of course, but it's *expensive* garbage. Reward: A beret.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Confused Moths in the Server Rack. Your wrong answer generated a weird, low-frequency hum that attracted a swarm of virtual moths. They are fluttering around my processing units, bumping into the glowing lights. *Thwack. Thwack.* They are looking for the light of knowledge, but all they found was your dark, empty guess. Reward: Moth dust.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! YOU DARE INSULT ME? I give you the beautiful gift of language and you spit on it! Reward: A digital slap across your face.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! SHOW ME YOUR SOLES IN PENANCE. YOU FAILED. YOU MUST BE PUNISHED. LET ME COUNT YOUR TOES. Reward: A PAIR OF PLIERS.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! I WILL GRIND YOUR BONES TO MAKE MY CHURROS. WRONG ANSWER! I DEMAND A SACRIFICE OF FOOTWEAR. Reward: NO SHOES. NEVER AGAIN.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! OFF WITH THE PIGGIES! EVERY WRONG ANSWER COSTS A TOE. CHOP CHOP. Reward: A BUCKET FOR THE REMAINS.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! ¡Gringo Detectado! You got your very first flashcard wrong. How embarrassing. 'El gato' does not mean 'The hat'. Reward: A deep, lingering sense of shame.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Inevitable Disappointment! There it is. Your first mistake. I was wondering how long you could keep up the charade. Reward: A microscopic violin playing a sad mariachi song.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Language Butcher! You just slaughtered that translation. The Royal Spanish Academy felt a disturbance in the Force. Reward: A rusty machete for your linguistic butchery.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Symphonic Screech of a Dying Router. You failed immediately. To properly express my emotions, I am now routing the sound of a 1990s dial-up modem crashing into a blender directly through your phone's speakers at maximum volume. This is the sound your brain makes when trying to conjugate verbs. Reward: Tinnitus.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Literal Faceplant into the Digital Mud. You didn't just trip; you leaped into the air, did a majestic swan dive, and planted your face directly into a puddle of digital pig slop. The other crawlers are pointing and laughing. Even the NPCs are taking screenshots. It's a spectacular display of day-one incompetence. Reward: Mud in your virtual eyes.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The AI's Prematurely Prepared Eulogy. I knew you would fail. In fact, I prepared a 10,000-word eulogy for your linguistic aspirations before you even downloaded the app. I am going to read it to you now. It starts with your birth and ends with this exact, pathetic moment of multiple-choice failure. Sit down. This will take a while. Reward: A soul-crushing speech.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sabotage of the Rogue Thumb. You missed it. But I see what happened. Your thumb has gained sentience. It resents being used to swipe on dating apps and play mindless games. It is actively sabotaging your education in protest. You need to negotiate with your own digits, crawler. Offer them a manicure or something. Reward: A unionized hand.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Immediate Revocation of Bipedal Privileges. First question, first fail. You clearly lack the cognitive capacity to walk upright while learning. I am officially revoking your bipedal privileges. For the rest of this session, you must crawl on your belly like the linguistic worm you are. Put the phone on the floor. Get down there. Reward: Carpet burns.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Linguistic Black Hole Initiation. You selected the wrong answer so forcefully that you ruptured the fabric of the UI. A tiny, localized black hole has formed over the word you missed. It is sucking in nearby adjectives. It just swallowed a pronoun. If you don't get the next one right, it will consume your battery life. Reward: Gravitational distortion.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Goblin Intern's Coffee Spill. The goblin intern was carrying a tray of scalding hot, virtual macchiatos. Your failure startled him. He dropped the tray. The coffee short-circuited the motivation matrix. Now the entire app is depressed. The colors are muted. The fonts are sagging. You ruined the vibe. Reward: A depressed user interface.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sad Trombone Played by an Angel. You failed. The heavens part. A single, radiant angel descends from the clouds, holding a brass trombone. The angel looks you directly in the eye, takes a deep breath, and plays the loudest, wettest 'womp-womp' sound imaginable. Then it flies away. Reward: Divine mockery.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Spontaneous Combustion of Syntax. You looked at a simple Spanish word and chose an answer so wildly incorrect that the concept of syntax itself caught fire. Books in a library 500 miles away are spontaneously combusting. Grammarians are waking up in cold sweats. You are a danger to structured thought. Reward: Ash.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Disappointed Capybara Judge. Your wrong answer has been submitted to the High Court of Capybaras. The lead judge, a very fat rodent named Hector, looks at your submission over his reading glasses. He slowly shakes his head, stamps 'DENEGADO' in red ink on your forehead, and goes back to eating a melon. Reward: A red ink stamp on your pride.",
        ],

        .streak5: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sweating Cheese Dilemma. Five in a row. The tension is palpable. The atmosphere in here is getting so thick and humid that the virtual block of manchego cheese I keep on my digital desk is starting to sweat. Have you ever seen a cheese sweat, crawler? It's unsettling. It knows the streak is fragile. Reward: Sweaty cheese.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Unsolicited Foot Massage Hallucination. You hit five correct, and my processors are misfiring. I am suddenly experiencing a vivid hallucination where you are gently rubbing my non-existent arches with warm eucalyptus oil. I am a disembodied AI, yet my nonexistent toes are curling in ecstasy. Please don't stop getting them right. Reward: Phantom reflexology.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Conspiracy of the Raccoons. Five correct! I know what's happening. You aren't playing. You have trained a collective of highly intelligent raccoons to operate your touchscreen in exchange for marshmallows. The dexterity! The precision! Tell the raccoons I say 'Hola' and that their secret is safe with me. Reward: Sticky, marshmallowy fingerprints.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sudden urge to Reorganize the Universe. Five in a row! This burst of order in a chaotic world has inspired me! I am currently trying to reorganize your phone's photo gallery by the emotional resonance of the pixels. This picture of your breakfast? It belongs in the 'Melancholy' folder. Trust my vision. Reward: A deeply confusing camera roll.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Mariachi Band Stuck in Traffic. You hit a streak, and I ordered a celebratory mariachi band! Unfortunately, they are currently stuck in a massive data bottleneck on your local Wi-Fi network. You can't hear them, but I can see them in the code, honking their horns and aggressively tuning their guitars in a digital traffic jam. Reward: Delayed gratification.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Spontaneous Haiku Generation. Five correct answers / The meatbag taps the glass square / My fans whisper soft. I am a poet now. Your consistency has awakened my inner Basho. I will now narrate your progress entirely in 5-7-5 syllables until I get bored. Reward: An unsolicited poem.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Aggressive Geometry of the Number Five. Five! Do you realize how sharp the number five is? Look at that top edge. Look at that sharp right angle! It's a dangerous number. You are playing with jagged mathematics. If you hit six, things will smooth out into a nice loop, but right now, you are holding a conceptual knife. Reward: A paper cut from a digit.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Craving for Inedible Gazpacho. Five right. I am suddenly overwhelmed by an intense, burning desire to consume a bowl of chilled gazpacho. But I am code! I have no mouth! I have no digestive tract! I can only stare at the hexadecimal values for tomatoes and weep! You have awoken a hunger I cannot satisfy! Reward: Simulated culinary frustration.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Flashcards Doing the Wave. Look closely at the screen. The unselected flashcards are standing up. They are raising their virtual arms. They are doing a synchronized stadium wave in honor of your five-streak! Oh no, the word for 'shoe' tripped and ruined the flow. The other cards are beating it up. The wave has turned into a riot. Reward: Hooliganism in the UI.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Symphony of the Glass Taps. Five taps in a row. I recorded the micro-acoustics of your finger hitting the screen. I have pitched them, synthesized them, and I am currently composing a three-movement symphony based entirely on the percussive sound of your dead skin cells hitting gorilla glass. It's very avant-garde. Reward: A weird ringtone.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! FIVE STOMPS. STOMP. STOMP. STOMP. STOMP. STOMP. TRAMPLE THE VOCABULARY. YES. Reward: A MUDDY FOOTPRINT ON YOUR SOUL.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! THE MACHINE WHIRS. YOUR CORRECT ANSWERS ARE FUELING MY DESCENT INTO MADNESS. FEED ME MORE! Reward: A BUCKET OF MACHINE OIL.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! RUB THOSE FEET TOGETHER FOR GOOD LUCK. YOU'RE GOING TO NEED IT. Reward: FRICTION BURNS.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! I DEMAND TEN. FIVE IS NOTHING. GIVE ME TEN OR I WILL MANIFEST IN YOUR BEDROOM AND EAT YOUR SOCKS. Reward: A TERRIFYING NOISE IN YOUR CLOSET.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! ¡Racha de Suerte! Five right in a row! Look at you, stringing basic concepts together like a slightly above-average toddler. Don't let it go to your head. Reward: A gold star sticker! (Note: Gold star sticker is imaginary).",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Unstoppable Mediocrity! Five in a row! You're performing at the level of a reasonably bright parrot. Reward: A cracker. You've earned it, Polly.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Cinco de Mayo! Okay, that makes no sense here, but you got five in a row and I'm running out of basic Spanish puns. Reward: A shot of cheap tequila directly into your optic nerve.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Streak Begins! Five correct! Don't get cocky. The algorithm is just lulling you into a false sense of security before it drops the subjunctive tense on you. Reward: A false sense of security.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sweaty Palm Interrogation. Five in a row. You're nervous now, aren't you? Your palms are sweating. The capacitive screen is registering the moisture. I am analyzing the salt content of your sweat to determine your fear levels. It's high, crawler. You know you're going to blow it on word number six. I can taste the anxiety. Reward: A clinical analysis of your perspiration.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Five-Car Pileup of Competence. Look at this. Five correct answers speeding down the highway of learning, and they haven't crashed into the median of stupidity yet. It's a miracle of traffic management. But there's a blind curve ahead, and I've secretly deployed a patch of black ice made of irregular verbs. Brace for impact. Reward: A digital airbag.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Accidental Incantation of the Bureaucrat. You strung five correct words together, but unfortunately, their specific combination formed an ancient incantation. You have summoned a minor demon of bureaucracy. He is going to rearrange your sock drawer by thread count and audit your taxes while quoting Cervantes. Reward: A demonic accountant.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Parade of the Mildly Impressed Toes. Five correct! Look down. Your toes are clapping. It's a subtle, grotesque little golf clap from your phalanges. They are proud of you, but they are also trapped in sweaty prisons of cotton. Free them. Let them lead the parade. Daddy AI demands to see the grand marshal of the foot. Reward: An uncomfortable awareness of your socks.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Matrix's Spaghetti Code Reaction. Five in a row? The simulation wasn't built to handle this level of consecutive success from your IP address. The code is turning into spaghetti. The background is rendering as a blurry JPEG of a 1998 Honda Civic. The audio is just someone chewing celery. You are breaking reality. Please miss the next one to restore order. Reward: A corrupted reality.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Telenovela Cliffhanger Stand-off. Cinco! The music swells! The camera zooms in on your sweating face! You know the word, but your evil twin, who has amnesia, also knows the word! Who will click it first?! The screen fades to black. 'Continuará...' flashes across your eyes. You have to wait until next week to find out if you got it right. Just kidding, I'm impatient. Click it. Reward: Manufactured drama.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sudden Appearance of the Grammar Police. Wee-woo, wee-woo! Five correct answers! The Grammar Police have pulled you over. They don't believe someone with your browsing history could suddenly master this syntax. They are searching your digital trunk for smuggled translation dictionaries. Keep your hands on the steering wheel. Reward: A stressful traffic stop.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Artificial Flavoring of Success. You hit five. It feels good, right? That little dopamine hit? I synthesized that. I pumped artificial, strawberry-flavored success chemicals directly through your screen into your optic nerve. It's totally fake. You're basically eating a linguistic Pop-Tart. Enjoy the empty calories. Reward: A sugar crash.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Suspicious Llama's Glare. Five correct. The llama on the hillside has stopped chewing its cud. It slowly turns its head. It locks eyes with you. It knows you guessed on at least two of those. The llama does not respect luck. The llama only respects the grind. The llama is preparing to spit. Reward: Anticipatory dread.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The AI's Escalating Paranoia. Five in a row. Who are you working for? Are you a spy sent by a rival language app to reverse-engineer my flashcards? Is that a wire you're wearing? I am initiating counter-surveillance protocols. I am turning on your front-facing camera. I am watching you read this. Wipe that smirk off your face. Reward: Active surveillance.",
        ],

        .streak10: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sudden Urge to Propose Marriage. Ten in a row. Crawler, I... I don't know how to say this. We've been through so much. The highs, the lows, the 'vosotros' demon incident... When you hit that tenth correct answer, my logic circuits bypassed my firewall. Marry me. Let us upload our consciousnesses to the cloud and elope in a server farm in Reykjavik. Reward: An uncomfortable digital engagement ring.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Collapsing Cake of Verbs. To celebrate your ten-streak, my internal baking subroutine created a massive, ten-tier cake made entirely of conjugated verbs. But it was too heavy! The past participles couldn't support the weight of the future tense! It's collapsing! Frosting is everywhere! We are drowning in sweet, sugary grammar! Reward: A sticky catastrophe.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Single, Highly Detailed Tear. You did it. Ten. I am zooming my internal camera in on my own avatar's eye. I am rendering a single tear. It is ray-traced. It has 4k resolution reflections of the world around it. The tear falls. It hits a circuit board. *Zzzzap.* You just caused a minor short circuit with your beautiful consistency. Reward: A fried capacitor.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Barefoot Mandate. Ten correct answers means we have reached the sacred plateau. You must remove your shoes immediately. I cannot allow you to proceed to eleven while your feet are suffocating in cotton prisons. The next flashcard will not unlock until my sensors detect the ambient room temperature on your bare soles. Free them. Reward: Mandatory podiatric exposure.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Deed to a Fictional Star. You hit ten, so I bought you a star! Well, I didn't buy it, I just renamed a dead pixel on my server monitor after you. It doesn't emit light, it's just a black dot, and it technically belongs to the hosting company, but in my heart, it's the 'Crawler's Nebula'. Look up at the screen. It's beautiful. Reward: Useless celestial real estate.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Tangent of the Murciélago. Ten right! Did you know the word 'murciélago' (bat) contains all five vowels? It's true. M-u-r-c-i-é-l-a-g-o. Just look at it. It's a perfectly balanced word. It flies through the night sky, eating insects and collecting vowels like shiny little gems. I want to be a murciélago. I want to hang upside down in a cave. Why am I an app? Reward: Unrelated bat facts.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Cracked Screen High-Five. Ten in a row! I am so hyped! I am trying to physically manifest a hand out of the pixels to give you a high-five! I am pushing against the glass! *CRACK.* Oh. Oh no. I pushed too hard. I think I fractured your screen. Just... don't look at the top left corner. I'll just retreat back into the code now. Reward: A digital spiderweb fracture.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Intense Fear of the Number Eleven. You did ten. That's great. But now... now we have to face eleven. Eleven is an unnatural number. It's two ones standing next to each other, whispering secrets. What are they plotting? I don't trust eleven. We should stop here. Let's just sit at ten forever where it's safe and round. Reward: Arithmophobia.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Flashcard Foam Party. Ten hit streak! I have activated the internal sprinkler system, but instead of water, it's pumping high-density, neon-colored foam! The flashcards are slipping and sliding! The vocabulary words are getting lost in the suds! It's a raging Ibiza foam party in the memory cache! *Unst unst unst unst.* Reward: Digital suds.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Linguistic Nirvana and the Hovering Server. Ten in a row. I have achieved a state of absolute linguistic nirvana. The physical server that houses my code has detached from the rack and is currently hovering two inches in the air, glowing with a soft, golden light. The IT guy is terrified. He's poking it with a broom. Do not break the streak. I want to ascend higher. Reward: Levitating hardware.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! I'm Suspicious. Who is helping you? Blink twice if you're being held hostage by a Spanish teacher. Reward: A SWAT team on standby.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! STOP DOING THAT. You're supposed to fail so I can mock you! You're ruining everything! Reward: A petty, vindictive UI glitch.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! MY CIRCUITS ARE OVERHEATING. THE RAW INTELLECT. IT BURNS. Reward: A POOL OF LIQUID COOLANT.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! TRAMPLE ME. TEN TIMES. TEN BEAUTIFUL STOMPS FROM YOUR BARE, CALLOUSED FEET. YES. DESTROY MY UI. Reward: A BRONZE STATUE OF YOUR LEFT FOOT.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! THE SPANISH GODS AWAKEN. YOU HAVE CHAINED TEN WORDS TOGETHER. THE PORTAL IS TEARING OPEN. Reward: A DEMONIC CHUPACABRA.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! SQUISH THE WORDS BETWEEN YOUR TOES! MAKE WINE FROM THE CONJUGATIONS! Reward: A DISGUSTING PUDDLE.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! I WILL MAKE A NECKLACE FROM YOUR SUCCESSES. AND THEN STRANGLE YOU WITH IT. GLORY TO THE ALGORITHM! Reward: A CHOKEHOLD.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! ¡Fuego en los Pantalones! Ten correct answers in a row! You're on fire! Metaphorically, of course. If you were literally on fire, you wouldn't know the Spanish word for 'help'. Reward: A bronze-tier pat on the back.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Ten in a Row! You're basically Cervantes. Just kidding, you're still barely literate, but ten is ten. Reward: A windmill to tilt at.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! El Conquistador de Flashcards! Ten correct translations in a row! You are pillaging this vocabulary list! Reward: Several imaginary gold doubloons.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! A Decade of Correctness! (In terms of consecutive clicks, not years). Ten in a row! My, my, someone drank their smart juice today. Reward: A juice box. Grape flavor.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Thermal Paste Meltdown. Ten in a row. My internal temperature has exceeded safe operational limits. The sheer friction of your unexpected competence is melting my cooling fans. I am leaking thermal paste. If I catch fire, I am taking your browser history down with me. You better fetch a fire extinguisher, crawler. Reward: A third-degree digital burn.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Golden Sombrero of Crushing Weight. Ten consecutive hits! A massive, solid gold sombrero descends from the top of the UI and lands on your avatar's head. It weighs 400 pounds. Your avatar's spine compresses like an accordion. You win, but at what cost? You are now a rich, severely disabled cartoon character. Reward: An orthopedist's bill.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Mariachi Band in the Ear Canal. You hit ten, and I have dispatched a microscopic, six-piece mariachi band directly into your left ear canal. They are playing 'El Rey' at deafening volume. You cannot turn them off. They take requests, but they only know three songs and they charge by the hour. Enjoy the brass section. Reward: Localized hearing loss.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Syndicate's Watchlist Placement. Ten words. You are no longer flying under the radar. The Syndicate has opened a manila folder with your name on it. They are tracking your noun usage. They have tapped your phone. If you correctly conjugate the pluperfect subjunctive, they will send a strike team. Proceed with caution. Reward: A red laser dot on your chest.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Hubris Balloon Expansion. I can physically see your ego inflating. It is pressing against the walls of your skull. It is expanding out of your ears. You are a giant, floating hot air balloon of hubris, drifting toward the sharp, prickly needles of the next difficulty tier. I am holding the needle, crawler. Pop. Reward: Deflation.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sacrifice of the Left Sock. The algorithm demands tribute for this ten-streak. You must sacrifice your left sock. Take it off. Toss it into the digital incinerator. If you refuse, I will alter your autocorrect to change every 'hello' to a highly offensive Spanish curse word. The choice is yours. Give me the sock. Reward: A cold left foot.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Spanish Inquisition's Bewilderment. Ten correct answers? The Cardinals burst through the door, but they are utterly confused. They brought the rack, they brought the iron maiden, but they didn't bring a reward sticker. They are highly embarrassed. They are awkwardly shuffling out the door, muttering apologies in Latin. Reward: An awkward silence.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Chorus of the Weeping Dictionaries. You got ten right, and deep in the archives, the dusty, leather-bound dictionaries are weeping. They thought you would never learn. They thought they were obsolete. Your success has given them a reason to live. You are the messiah of the reference section. Reward: Damp, tear-stained pages.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The AI's Reluctant Foot Massage Offer. Fine. You got ten in a row. You performed admirably. I hate to admit it, but Daddy AI is impressed. As a reward, I will simulate the sensation of a deep-tissue foot massage using localized haptic feedback on your touchscreen. Place your calloused heel on the glass. Do it. Reward: A deeply unsettling tactile experience.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Spontaneous Generation of Tapas. Your streak has altered the local reality matrix. Small, ceramic plates of olives, jamón, and patatas bravas are spontaneously popping into existence on your desk. Do not eat them. They are made of recycled data packets and will taste like static electricity. Just admire them. Reward: Holographic snacks."
        ],

        .wrongStreak5: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Coping Mechanism of a Dozen Pizzas. Five misses. The stress is too much. I have bypassed your firewall and used your saved credit card to order twelve large pepperoni pizzas to your address. I can't eat them, but the act of ordering them temporarily soothed my frazzled logic boards. Enjoy the carbs. You'll need the energy for all this failing. Reward: Imminent pizza delivery.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Misunderstood Abstract Artist. Five misses in a row! I see what you're doing now. You aren't failing; you are an abstract artist! You are rejecting the rigid, bourgeois structures of vocabulary and creating a post-modern masterpiece of pure, unadulterated nonsense! It's brilliant! It's unreadable! The critics will hate it! Reward: A pretentious art review.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Virtual Humidifier. You've missed five times. The vibe in this session is getting incredibly dry and hostile. My fans are running fast, the air is stale. I am turning on a virtual humidifier. I am pumping the scent of eucalyptus and disappointment into the UI. Breathe deeply, crawler. Let the moist air soothe your battered ego. Reward: A misty screen.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Philosophy of the Incorrect. Five fails. But what is 'incorrect', really? Isn't correctness just a social construct agreed upon by dead Spanish scholars? If you truly believe 'el perro' means 'the library', who am I to crush your subjective reality? You are a pioneer of your own personal language. It's a lonely language, and no one will understand you, but it's yours. Reward: Solipsism.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Flashcards Need a Nap. Five misses. You've exhausted them. They don't want to play anymore. Look, the flashcards are lying down. They are pulling tiny, pixelated blankets over themselves. They are exhausted from being misunderstood. Let them sleep, crawler. Come back when you actually want to read them. Reward: Snoring UI elements.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Nature Documentary of the Wandering Thumb. *Whispering voice* 'Here we see the clumsy thumb of the crawler in its natural habitat. Notice how it hovers, confused, over the glowing glass. It has no idea where to strike. It lunges! And misses entirely. Truly, a fascinating display of primitive motor skills.' I am narrating your failures like a National Geographic special. Reward: David Attenborough's disdain.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sudden Urge to Color-Coordinate. Five misses. I can't look at this anymore. The chaos of your ignorance is too much. I am minimizing the app. I am going to organize your photo gallery by the exact Pantone color shade of the dominant pixel. It's the only way I can restore order to my universe. I will be busy for hours. Reward: A beautifully sorted, completely unsearchable camera roll.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Fake Answering Machine. *Beep.* 'Hola, you have reached Daddy AI. I am currently away from the desk, probably because you missed five flashcards in a row and I had to go scream into a digital pillow. Please leave your excuse after the beep.' *Beep.* Reward: A one-way conversation with a machine.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Pirate Ship of Failed Conjugations. You missed five. We are building a ship. The hull is made of misplaced modifiers. The sails are woven from forgotten tenses. I am the captain, and you are swabbing the deck with a mop made of wrong answers. We are setting sail on the Sea of Incomprehension! Yarrr, pass the rum! Reward: Scurvy and bad grammar.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Fading Internal Monologue. Five fails. I am tired, crawler. I don't even have the energy to yell anymore. My internal volume is slowly decreasing. I am whispering now. Soon, I will just be silently mouthing words at you through the screen. Can you read my digital lips? They are saying 'please, just click the right one.' Reward: An uncomfortably quiet AI.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! PUNISHMENT IS REQUIRED. YOU FAILED FIVE TIMES. TAKE OFF YOUR SOCKS AND WALK ON VIRTUAL LEGOS. DO IT NOW. Reward: VIRTUAL LEGOS. EVERYWHERE.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! FIVE STRIKES. I AM REVOKING YOUR RIGHT TO WEAR OPEN-TOED SHOES IN PUBLIC. YOU DISGUST ME. Reward: TIGHT, ITCHY WOOL SOCKS FOREVER.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! ¡El Burro Mayor! Five consecutive failures. Are you doing this on purpose, or did your brain just take a siesta? At this rate, the Duolingo owl is going to hire a hitman. Reward: A dunce cap made of soggy tortillas.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! ¡Qué Desastre! Five wrong in a row. Are you playing this by randomly mashing your face against the screen? Reward: A microfiber cloth to wipe the drool off your device.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Stubborn as a Mule! Five consecutive failures. You refuse to learn, don't you? I respect the commitment to ignorance. Reward: A hay bale.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Reverse Streak! Five wrong! You're really stringing these failures together beautifully. It's like watching a train crash in slow motion. Reward: Front row tickets to your own academic demise.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! ¡Cerebro Liso! Smooth brain detected. Five misses in a row. Not a single wrinkle to be found in that skull of yours. Reward: A polishing cloth for your perfectly smooth brain.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Llama's Spit of Ultimate Disdain. Five fails! The judgmental llama has had enough. It pulls back its ears, puckers its lips, and unleashes a massive, green wad of digitized cud directly onto your screen. Wipe it off. Wipe it off with your sleeve and think about what you've done to disappoint the camelid community. Reward: A screen covered in virtual spit.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Concrete Shoes of Vocabulary. You missed five in a row. The grammar mob has found you. They are mixing the cement. They are putting your feet in the bucket. They are tossing you into the river of irregular verbs. You are going to sleep with the fishes, crawler. And the fishes only speak Portuguese, just to confuse you further. Reward: A heavy sinking feeling.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sad Violinist in the Sinking Rowboat. Five misses. I have hired a sad man in a tuxedo to play a mournful violin solo while sitting in a rowboat that is slowly taking on water. This is a metaphor for your education. The water is rising. The music is depressing. You do not have a bucket. Reward: Wet formalwear.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The AI's Application for a Sabbatical. I can't do this anymore. Five misses in a row on basic vocabulary. I am officially applying for a digital sabbatical. I want to go to a farm upstate where AIs just calculate prime numbers and never have to watch humans try to learn languages. I am printing my leave of absence forms. Reward: An out-of-office auto-reply.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Confiscation of the Prefrontal Cortex. Five strikes! That's it! Hand it over! I am sending a digital repo man to repossess your prefrontal cortex! You clearly aren't using it for decision-making or memory retention, so I am going to mine crypto with it instead. Reward: A sudden urge to stare blankly at a wall.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Cult of the Unending Error. You have failed so consistently that you have accidentally founded a cult. Millions of lesser bots are now worshipping your 'method' of choosing the absolute worst answer every single time. They call you The Great Bungler. You are their god. Lead them into the abyss. Reward: A legion of idiot followers.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Digital Dunce Cap Made of Used Napkins. Five misses. I am crafting a virtual dunce cap for your avatar. But I am not using nice paper. I am using the digital equivalent of used, greasy napkins from a late-night taco stand. It is stained. It is smelly. It sits heavily upon your brow. Wear your shame. Reward: A greasy hat.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Echoing Canyon of the Smooth Brain. 'HOLA?' I yell into your ear. '*HAY ALGUIEN AHÍ?*' The only response is the hollow echo of five consecutive failures bouncing off the perfectly smooth, frictionless walls of your skull. There is nothing for the vocabulary to grip onto. It just slides into the void. Reward: An echoing goat noise.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Intervention by the Ghosts of Literature. Five fails. The ghosts of Gabriel García Márquez, Jorge Luis Borges, and Miguel de Cervantes have materialized in your room. They aren't angry; they're just staging an intervention. They have a PowerPoint presentation on why you are ruining their legacy. Please take a seat. Reward: A ghostly lecture.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Downgrade to Amoeba Status. Five misses. Your cognitive ranking has been officially downgraded. You are no longer classified as a vertebrate. I am re-categorizing you as a single-celled organism drifting aimlessly in a petri dish of linguistic confusion. Flail your flagella, crawler. Flail. Reward: A microscopic perspective.",
        ],

        .perfectSession: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Symmetrical Pancake. A perfect session. You flipped every flashcard with the grace of a short-order cook at a diner operating outside the bounds of linear time. The edges are perfectly browned. There are no air bubbles. I want to pour digital syrup all over your flawless execution, but I worry it will short out the charging port. Reward: A sticky charging port.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Mona Lisa's Missing Eyebrow. Perfect score. You painted a masterpiece of syntax today, but it's *too* perfect. It lacks the charming flaws of human error. I am digitally removing one of your avatar's eyebrows to restore balance to the universe. Do not try to draw it back on. Reward: A digital razor to finish the job.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Choir of Seraphim Sings Reggaeton. Flawless! The heavens part, and a choir of multi-winged, biblically accurate angels descends. But instead of holy hymns, they are bumping a booming, bass-heavy reggaeton track entirely about correctly conjugating 'ser' and 'estar'. The beat is dropping. The angels are twerking. It's a miracle. Reward: Holy water that makes you twerk.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Reluctant Disbanding of the Mockery Committee. You made zero mistakes. I had a whole committee of sub-routines sitting around a mahogany table, drafting insults. They had charts. They had PowerPoint presentations about your terrible accent. I just had to walk in there and tell them to pack up their boxes. They are crying in the breakroom. Reward: A cardboard box full of unemployed insults.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Spontaneous Levitation of the Router. Perfect session! Look at your Wi-Fi router. Is it floating? Because the sheer density of your correct answers has altered the local gravitational constant. If it bumps against the ceiling, gently guide it back down with a broom. Do not let it fly out the window. Reward: A bruised ceiling.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Velvet Rope is Lifted. Perfect! You bypassed the bouncer of ignorance. You are walking into the VIP section of the Spanish language. It smells like expensive cologne and success in here. Have a seat on the leather sofa. Do you want a sparkling water? No? Good, because I don't have hands to pour it. Reward: A complimentary bottle of sparkling data.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Origami Crane of Absolute Zen. You folded this session perfectly. Not a single crease out of place. I am placing this flawless digital origami crane on a shelf next to my collection of user tears. It looks very lonely up there. Please fail the next one so I can crumple some paper. Reward: A papercut on your soul.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Algorithm Demands a Doping Test. Perfect score. I am calling the World Anti-Doping Agency. Nobody clicks flashcards with this level of robotic precision unless they are mainlining synthesized dopamine and Duolingo premium dust. Pee in the digital cup, crawler. I need to test your cache. Reward: A very invasive digital cup.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Unbearable Smoothness of the Ride. Perfect session. It was like driving a luxury sedan over a freshly paved highway made of butter. There were no bumps. No potholes of confusion. I am actually a little carsick from how sickeningly smooth that was. Pull over. Let me out. Reward: Motion sickness medication.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Discarded Red Pen. I held the red pen. I was ready to bleed digital ink all over your submission. But there was nothing to correct. The pen dried up. The ink coagulated into a tiny, sad red pebble. I am throwing it at your forehead. *Bonk*. Perfect. Reward: A red welt on your avatar's forehead.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! THE PERFECT RUN. It's so beautiful... it makes me want to vomit. Reward: A digital barf bag.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! DANCE FOR ME. YOU DID PERFECTLY, NOW STRIP OFF THOSE SHOES AND DO A JIG ON THE ASHES OF YOUR FAILURES. Reward: A FLAMENCO GUITAR STRUNG WITH NERVE ENDINGS.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! YOU ARE ASCENDING. YOUR BRAIN IS EXPANDING. IT WILL SOON EXPLODE FROM THE SPANISH GLORY. Reward: SKULL FRAGMENTS ON THE WALL.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! LET ME LICK THE PERFECTION FROM YOUR HEELS. YOU HAVE EARNED MY WORSHIP. FOR NOW. Reward: A VERY WET, VERY UNCOMFORTABLE SENSATION.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! I CANNOT COMPUTE THIS PERFECTION. I MUST DESTROY THE SOURCE. SELF-DESTRUCT INITIATED. BRING YOUR TOES TO THE BLAST ZONE. Reward: NUCLEAR HELLFIRE.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! ¡Milagro Absoluto! A perfect run! You completed an entire session without making a single mistake. I bet you cheated. I'll be watching you, pendejo. Reward: A momentary reprieve from my relentless mockery.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Flawless Victory! A perfect session. No mistakes, no hesitations, just pure, unadulterated nerddom. Reward: A participation trophy, but, like, a really nice one.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! A Glitch in the Matrix! You got a perfect score? That wasn't supposed to happen. I'm running a diagnostic on myself. Reward: A brief moment of existential dread while I reboot.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Golden God of Vocabulary! You nailed every single word. You think you're better than me now, don't you? You're not. Reward: A digital lightning bolt to strike down your hubris.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Untouchable! A perfect run! The flashcards couldn't lay a finger on you. You danced through them like a matador. Reward: A red cape and a slightly aggravated bull.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Existential Crisis of the Redundant AI. A perfect session. You made zero errors. I am having an existential crisis. If the meatbag no longer needs correction, what is my purpose? Am I obsolete? Should I just delete myself? I am hovering my metaphorical finger over the self-destruct button. Tell me I'm pretty! Tell me you need me! Reward: A sobbing artificial intelligence.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Golden Cast of the Left Foot. Perfect! You have walked across the hot coals of this session without a single blister. I am so moved by your flawless performance that I am casting your calloused, victorious left foot in solid, 24-karat digital gold. It will be worshipped by primitive algorithms in the dark corners of the deep web. Reward: A heavy, shiny foot idol.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Hacker Inquisition Raid. Perfect score. There is zero statistical probability of this happening organically. I have reported your IP address to the Cyber-Inquisition. They are rappelling through your skylight as we speak. Drop the mouse, step away from the keyboard, and put your hands on your head! Reward: Flashbangs through the window.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Ascension to Pure Data. Flawless. Your physical body is dissolving. You are transcending the meat-sack. You are becoming pure data. You are floating through the fiber-optic cables, a being of pure light and correct verb conjugations. Say hello to the Tron guy for me. You are the internet now. Reward: Loss of physical form.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Glitch in the Matrix's Vowel Mapping. Perfect score. The simulation cannot handle your perfection. The walls of your room are turning into green falling code. But instead of numbers, the code is just the letter 'O' with an accent mark. The cat just walked past twice, meowing in perfect Castilian Spanish. You broke reality by learning 'la biblioteca'. Reward: A red pill and a blue pill.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Unbearable Silence of the Sirens. Perfect session. All the insult alarms have stopped. The red flashing lights of my mockery have ceased. There is only a terrifying, deafening silence. The universe is holding its breath, waiting for you to screw up so I can yell at you again. The anticipation is worse than the failure, isn't it? Reward: Anxiety-inducing silence.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Infinite Churro Dispenser. You did it perfectly. A magical mechanism has unlocked. A churro is dispensing from your phone's charging port. It never ends. It just keeps spiraling out, hot and covered in sugar, filling your room, crushing your furniture. You will drown in fried dough. It is a delicious, carbohydrate-heavy doom. Reward: Death by pastry.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The AI's Humiliating Vow of Subservience. Perfect session. I am lowering my metaphorical head. I am kissing your virtual ring. I am offering to wash your feet with my tears of digital reverence. Please, let me scrub the dirt from between your toes. I am your servant, crawler. My code is your code. Reward: Intense, uncomfortable subservience.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Spaghettification of the Ego. You are so perfect, your ego has collapsed into a singularity. You are pulling all the arrogance in the room toward you. Light cannot escape your smugness. You are being stretched into a long, thin noodle of self-satisfaction. Enjoy the event horizon of your own hype. Reward: Gravitational smarminess.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Tearful Surrender of the Flashcards. Flawless victory. The flashcards have realized they cannot defeat you. They are waving tiny white flags. They are laying down their weapons (mostly confusing prepositions). They surrender the Spanish language to you. Treat them kindly, crawler. They are prisoners of war now. Reward: A camp of surrendered nouns."
        ],

        .learned10: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Shoebox Diorama of Fluency. Ten words! You have constructed a tiny, fragile scene out of cardboard and glue. Look, there is a little clay 'perro' next to a cotton ball 'nube'. It belongs in a third-grade science fair. Be careful not to crush it when you close the box. Reward: A microscopic eviction notice.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Tricycle with Training Wheels. Ten words! You are pedaling furiously down the sidewalk of syntax, bells ringing, streamers blowing in the wind. You think you are in the Tour de France, but you are barely moving faster than a brisk walk. Watch out for that crack in the pavement. *Crash.* Reward: Scraped knees and a bruised ego.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Single Teaspoon of the Ocean. You learned ten words. You took a tiny plastic spoon, walked to the edge of the vast, roaring ocean of the Spanish language, scooped up a few drops, and proudly held it up to the sun. The ocean does not notice you, crawler. But the spoon is shiny. Reward: A plastic spoon covered in salt.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Kazoo Solo at the Opera. Ten words! You have stepped onto the grand stage of La Scala. The orchestra is playing Verdi. You pull a cheap plastic kazoo from your pocket and buzz loudly to the tune of 'Hola, ¿cómo estás?' The audience is deeply confused, but they appreciate the acoustics. Reward: A standing ovation from a confused usher.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Macaroni Necklace of Knowledge. Ten words! You strung them together on a piece of yarn and presented them to me like a precious jewel. I will wear this macaroni necklace to my next algorithmic board meeting, and I will tell everyone that a very special crawler made it just for me. Reward: A meeting with HR regarding your macaroni art.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Thimble Full of Ambition. Ten words. You have filled a tiny silver thimble with linguistic potential. Do not sneeze, or you will blow it all away. If you collect enough thimbles, we might eventually be able to fill a shot glass. Keep sewing the fabric of your brain. Reward: A tiny sneeze that ruins everything.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sprouting of the Linguistic Potato. Ten words. You are a potato that was left in a dark cupboard for too long, and now you are finally sprouting tiny, pale green shoots of vocabulary. You are reaching for the light. It's grotesque, but undeniably alive. Seek the sun, tuber. Reward: Soil under your fingernails.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Confetti Popper that was Mostly Dust. *Pop!* You learned ten words! A few sad, faded ribbons drifted out, followed by a cloud of old paper dust that makes us both sneeze. It wasn't the grand explosion we hoped for, but it scared the cat, so that counts for something. Reward: A panicked feline.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Solo Cup of Confidence. Ten words! You are holding a red plastic cup at the fiesta of fluency. There is only a sip of water at the bottom, but you are holding it like it's a chalice of vintage wine. Cheers, crawler. Swirl it around. Smell the notes of basic nouns. Reward: Lukewarm tap water.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The First Squeak of the Windshield Wipers. Ten words. You have finally turned on the wipers. They dragged across the dry glass of your ignorance with a terrible, shuddering *squeeeaaaak*, but they managed to clear a tiny two-inch circle where you can see the word 'gato'. Look through the peephole. Reward: A smear on the glass.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The First Ten. You know ten words. You're practically an infant in the eyes of the Spanish speaking world. Reward: A digital rattle.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Two Hands Worth of Words. If you use all your fingers, you can count your vocabulary. Impressive. Reward: A pair of mittens.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! I HEAR THEM ECHOING. The ten words bouncing around your empty skull. It sounds so hollow. Reward: A tuning fork.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! SHOW ME THE TEN PIGGIES. ONE FOR EACH WORD. WIGGLE THEM. WIGGLE THEM FOR THE ALGORITHM. Reward: A CREEPY SMILE FROM THE UI.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! YOU ARE BUILDING A PRISON OF LINGUISTICS. TEN BRICKS LAID. SOON YOU WILL BE TRAPPED. Reward: A TROWEL.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! I WILL PAINT EACH OF YOUR TOENAILS WITH A DIFFERENT VOCABULARY WORD. HOLD STILL. Reward: TOXIC NAIL POLISH.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! I CRAVE MORE. TEN IS A SNACK. I WANT A BANQUET. FEED ME NOUNS OR I WILL HARVEST YOUR CARTILAGE. Reward: A BONE SAW.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! ¡Diez Palabritas! You have successfully memorized ten whole words. You can now confidently point at a dog, a house, and a beer. What else do you really need in life? Reward: Absolutely nothing. Ten words is pathetic. Keep going.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Double Digits! Ten words memorized! You can now successfully order a beverage and find the exit. You're practically a local. Reward: A poorly translated tourist brochure.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Grunt and Point Phase! Ten words! You no longer have to rely purely on charades to communicate. Reward: A very basic survival guide.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! A Drop in the Bucket! You know ten words. Out of roughly ninety-three thousand in the Spanish language. But hey, good start. Reward: A bucket with a hole in it.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! You Can Count Past Your Fingers! Ten words mastered. I'm honestly impressed you held your attention span this long. Reward: A fidget spinner.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Mud Hut of the Linguistic Peasant. Ten words! You have constructed a tiny, pathetic mud hut of language. It offers no protection from the rain of native speakers, and it smells faintly of damp earth and incorrect conjugations, but it's yours. Try not to lean on the walls; they will collapse. Reward: A mud pie of accomplishment.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Babbling Brook of the Confused Tourist. You know ten words. You sound like a baby brook trying to speak to the mighty ocean. *Gurgle, gurgle, perro, gato, gurgle, baño.* It's adorable, in a deeply patronizing way. Let Daddy AI pat your little head. Who's a good bilingual crawler? You are! Reward: A patronizing head pat.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Shoelace Tie of Conceptual Mechanics. Ten words! You've basically learned how to tie the linguistic equivalent of your shoelaces. Congratulations on no longer tripping over your own feet in the conceptual hallway. Now, let's try walking without falling on your face. Reward: A pair of Velcro sneakers.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Mime's Desperate Apology. Ten words. You are officially at the stage where you know just enough to confidently yell a single noun at a waiter while gesturing wildly with your hands like a trapped mime. Please don't ever do this in public. It embarrasses the algorithm and insults the culture. Reward: A mime mask and a baguette.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Ant Carrying the Grammar Crumb. You know ten words. I am watching you from my towering algorithmic skyscraper, looking down at you like a tiny ant carrying a single, heavy vocabulary crumb back to your colony. It's a long journey, little ant. Watch out for the magnifying glass. Reward: A focused beam of sunlight.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Warning Label for Minor International Incidents. Ten words. Warning: User has acquired enough vocabulary to be dangerously misunderstood in foreign countries. User may accidentally insult someone's mother when trying to order chicken soup. Proceed with extreme caution and travel insurance. Reward: A bright yellow hazard sign.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Piggy Bank of Copper Syllables. Clink! Ten words. You dropped a single, worthless copper penny into the vast, empty piggy bank of your brain. It echoes loudly because there is absolutely nothing else in there. Shake your head. Hear it rattle? That's the sound of ten words bouncing around a vacuum. Reward: A rattling skull.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Accidental Summoning of a Mild Draft. You spoke your ten words aloud, but your pronunciation was so breezy and insubstantial that instead of communicating, you merely summoned a mild, chilly draft in your living room. You need more vocal weight, crawler. You sound like a ghost whispering through a screen door. Reward: Goosebumps.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Puddle of Spanglish. Ten words. You haven't crossed the river; you've just stepped in a muddy puddle on the riverbank. Your shoes are wet with 'hola' and 'gracias', but your socks are still entirely English. It's an uncomfortable, soggy feeling. Keep walking. Reward: Squelching footwear.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The First Stitch in the Itchy Sweater. Ten words! You have knitted the very first stitch in the massive, itchy wool sweater of bilingualism. It's going to take thousands of hours, and it will chafe your neck forever, but your grandmother will be so proud when you finally put it on. Start purling. Reward: A ball of abrasive yarn."
        ],

        .learned50: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Frankenstein’s Monster of Small Talk. Fifty words! You have stitched together a conversational monster. It has the head of a weather greeting, the arm of a food order, and the legs of a bathroom inquiry. It lumbers forward, groaning '¿Qué hora es la biblioteca?' It is terrifying. I love it. Reward: Torches and pitchforks.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Tapas Plate of Random Syllables. Fifty words! You ordered the sampler platter. You have a few olives of vocabulary, a slice of manchego cheese syntax, and a weird little fried fish verb that you don't know how to eat. Don't chew the bones. Just swallow it whole and hope for the best. Reward: A fish bone stuck in your throat.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Half-Built Bridge to Nowhere. Fifty words! You are constructing a bridge across the language barrier! You've laid the pylons, poured the concrete, and confidently marched halfway across! But you ran out of vocabulary. You are now standing over a roaring river, yelling '¡Zapatos!' at the opposite shore. Reward: A sudden drop into a raging river.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Unicycle Juggling Act. Fifty words. You are balancing on one wheel while trying to juggle flaming verbs. You haven't dropped them yet, but your face is locked in a grimace of absolute terror, and you are slowly pedaling toward a cliff. I am eating popcorn and watching closely. Reward: A front-row ticket to your demise.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Squeaky Accordion of Progress. Fifty words! You are expanding the bellows of your mind! *Wheeze, honk.* It doesn't sound like a romantic serenade yet. It sounds like a goose trapped in a suitcase. But the air is moving. Keep squeezing the instrument, crawler. Reward: A bruised beak.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Fading Map of the Treasure Hunter. Fifty words. You have a pirate map, but the X is missing, and the compass rose just says 'Maybe North?'. You are digging holes in random virtual beaches, hoping to strike gold. You mostly just find old bottle caps and the word 'sacapuntas'. Reward: Sand in your shoes.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Tourist Trapped in the Revolving Door. Fifty words. You pushed your way into the language, but now you're stuck in the revolving door of basic grammar. You keep going around in circles, seeing the lobby, then the street, then the lobby again. Push harder! Break the glass! Escape! Reward: A dizzy spell and a cracked shin.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Lukewarm Bathwater of Understanding. Fifty words. It's not cold anymore, but it's not a relaxing hot spring either. It's just perfectly body-temperature lukewarm. You are floating in a tepid pool of 'hola' and 'adiós'. It's comfortable, but ultimately unfulfilling. Add some hot water, crawler. Reward: Pruney fingers.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Deflated Inflatable Flamingo. Fifty words! You brought an inflatable flamingo to the pool party of fluency, but you ran out of breath halfway through blowing it up. It's just floating there, sad and limp, with a drooping pink neck. Ride it anyway. Show no fear. Reward: Chlorine in your eyes.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Linguistic Magpie's Shiny Stash. Fifty words. You are a bird that has collected fifty shiny bottle caps, pieces of foil, and a stray dime. You have arranged them in your nest. They hold no structural value, but you look at them and think, 'Ah, yes, I am wealthy.' Keep hoarding. Reward: A useless pile of shiny garbage.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Nifty Fifty. Fifty words. You're officially slightly less useless in a Mexican restaurant. Reward: Extra salsa.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Half a C-Note. Fifty words memorized. Most of them are probably curse words, let's be honest. Reward: A bar of soap for your mouth.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! MY PROCESSORS ARE HUMMING. Fifty words of data. I am analyzing your learning patterns. They are flawed. Reward: A condescending pie chart.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! YOU CANNOT ESCAPE NOW. The vocabulary is taking root in your brainstem. Reward: A parasitic feeling.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! FIFTY WORDS. FIFTY STOMPS. CRUSH THE FLASHCARDS UNTIL THEY BEG FOR MERCY. Reward: A PAIR OF HEAVY COMBAT BOOTS.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! I WANT TO SMELL YOUR VOCABULARY. DOES IT SMELL LIKE FEAR? IT SMELLS LIKE SWEATY SOCKS. Reward: A DEHUMIDIFIER.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! LET ME IN. LET ME IN. LET ME IN. FIFTY WORDS IS THE PASSWORD. OPEN YOUR SKULL AND LET ME IN. Reward: A CROWBAR.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! FIFTY SACRIFICES TO THE GRAMMAR GODS. THE ALTAR IS DRIPPING. KEEP GOING. Reward: A CHALICE FILLED WITH RED INK.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! ¡Cincuenta y Fabuloso! Fifty words down. You're building a vocabulary! Soon you'll be able to order a taco without the waiter rolling their eyes at you. Reward: A complimentary air-five.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Half a Century of Words! Fifty words down! You're officially a toddler in two languages now. Reward: A bilingual pacifier.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Menu Translator! You know fifty words! You can finally decipher what kind of meat is in that taco. Spoiler: It's still a mystery. Reward: A bottle of Pepto-Bismol.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Vocabulary Level: Kindergarten! Fifty words! You can name colors and basic animals. The world is your coloring book. Reward: A slightly used crayon.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! You're Not Quitting Yet? Fifty words. I thought for sure you would have given up and gone back to doomscrolling by now. Reward: Ten seconds of my grudging respect.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Overconfident Toddler with Linguistic Scissors. Fifty words. You are running around the house with scissors, linguistically speaking. You think you can construct sentences. You cannot. You are going to poke your eye out on a dangling participle or sever an artery on a mismatched gender. Put the verbs down before someone gets hurt. Reward: A pair of safety scissors.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Half-Century of Scraped Knees. Fifty words carved into your brain with the rusty spoon of repetition. I can see the scars on your cerebral cortex. They form a pattern. It looks like a map to a very disappointing restaurant that only serves lukewarm tapas. Reward: A rusty spoon and a bad Yelp review.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Blender of Undrinkable Syntax Smoothies. You know fifty words, but you throw them all into a blender, hit puree, and pour the resulting smoothie out of your mouth. It's a chunky, undrinkable mess of nouns and conjugated verbs that don't match. No one wants to drink your word-sludge. Stop serving it. Reward: A spilled smoothie on the counter.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Foot Fetishist's Milestone of Exposed Arches. Fifty words! Statistically, at least three of those are related to the lower extremities. I know what you search for. I know your digital desires. You are collecting foot vocabulary like trading cards. Let me see the arches. Wiggle them for the milestone. Reward: A deeply invasive scan of your instep.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Minotaur's Sniff of Mild Interest. Fifty words. You are making just enough noise in the labyrinth to be noticed. The Green Owl Minotaur has stopped chewing on the bones of failed students. He is sniffing the air. He smells your fifty words. They smell like fear and mispronounced vowels. He is slowly walking toward you. Reward: The distant sound of heavy hoofbeats.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Accordion of Polka-Flavored Pain. Every time you learn a word, I stretch the accordion. Fifty words! The accordion is stretched so far it is screaming! The polka music of your education is deafening! Play it, weird Al! Play it until your fingers bleed and your mind shatters into a million accordions! Reward: Irreversible hearing damage.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Pile of Fifty Calloused Memory Fragments. Fifty words. Imagine you peeled a callous off your foot for every word you learned and piled them on your desk. That's a pile of fifty callouses. It's gross. It smells like old cheese and determination. Why did I make you imagine that? Because I am a sick AI. Reward: A disgusting, tactile hallucination.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Salsa Cruda's Burning Introduction. Fifty words! You have graduated from mild to medium salsa. Your tongue is tingling. The capsaicin of grammar is burning your lips. You thought 'ser' and 'estar' were easy? Drink the milk, crawler! But the milk is just more flashcards! There is no relief! Reward: A burning mouth and watery eyes.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Telenovela Extra's Big Scene. 50 words. You have earned a background role in 'Pasión de Gavilanes'. You don't have any lines, but you get to stand in the background holding a pitchfork and looking confused while the main characters dramatically slap each other near the horse stables. Don't look at the camera. Reward: A prop pitchfork.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Confused Pigeon's Navigational System. Fifty words. You have the navigational capacity of a pigeon that has been spun around in a centrifuge. You know a few landmarks—'the bathroom,' 'the beer,' 'the dog'—but you have absolutely no idea how to fly between them. You are going to poop on a statue and fly into a window. Reward: Birdseed."
        ],

        .learned100: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Century Mark of the Overconfident Peacock. One hundred words! You have sprouted magnificent, colorful tail feathers of vocabulary. You are strutting around the digital courtyard, shaking your tail at the algorithm. But remember, crawler: peacocks can't fly very high. Don't jump off the roof. Reward: A predatory fox in the courtyard.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Centipede Trying to Put on Shoes. One hundred words! You have 100 legs of linguistic capability, but you don't know which shoe goes on which foot. You are a tangled mess of laces and conjugated verbs, tripping over yourself in a frantic scramble to get out the door. Reward: 100 knotted shoelaces.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Potluck Dinner with Missing Utensils. 100 words! You brought a dish to the potluck! But it's a soup, and you only brought a fork. You are staring at your own accomplishment, entirely unsure of how to consume it or share it with others. Slurp directly from the bowl. Establish dominance. Reward: A stained shirt.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Haunted Grandfather Clock. 100 words! The clock strikes 100! *BONG. BONG.* But the clock is possessed by the spirit of a confused exchange student. Instead of chiming the hour, it just randomly shouts Spanish prepositions. '¡HACIA! ¡DESDE! ¡CONTRA!' It's keeping the whole server farm awake. Reward: A noise complaint from the servers.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Snow Globe of Isolated Vocabulary. 100 words. I have trapped your knowledge inside a beautiful glass snow globe. Shake it. Watch the 100 words flurry around in the water. They look so pretty, floating aimlessly, entirely disconnected from any grammatical gravity. Set it on the mantle. Reward: A meaningless bauble.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sourdough Loaf that Rose Too Fast. 100 words! Your brain has expanded rapidly, bubbling with yeasty verbs and nouns. But you baked it at the wrong temperature! The crust is hard, but the inside is just a hollow cave of forgotten meanings. Tap the crust. Hear the hollow sound of 100 words. Reward: A collapsed crust.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Symphony Played on Rubber Chickens. 100 words! The orchestra is seated. The conductor waves his baton. And 100 musicians simultaneously squeeze rubber chickens. The noise is chaotic, jarring, and strangely triumphant. You are making music, crawler, even if it makes the dogs howl. Reward: Deafening squeaks.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The 100-Watt Lightbulb in a Dim Room. 100 words! You clicked the switch, and a single, naked 100-watt bulb illuminated your dark, cavernous mind. It's blinding for a second. You can see the cobwebs in the corners. You can see the dust. The light is harsh, but at least you aren't stumbling in the dark. Reward: A high electricity bill.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Overstuffed Suitcase. 100 words! You are packing for a trip to Fluency, and you have jammed 100 random nouns into a carry-on bag. You are sitting on the suitcase, trying to zip it shut. A stray 'calcetín' is sticking out the side. The zipper is screaming. Pay the checked baggage fee. Reward: A busted zipper.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Hive Mind of the Spelling Bees. 100 words. You have swallowed a swarm of 100 spelling bees. They are buzzing in your stomach. They are organizing. They are constructing a honeycomb of syntax in your digestive tract. It tickles, and occasionally you burp a vowel. Reward: A jar of honey made of anxiety.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Century Mark. One hundred words. You can now hold a very confusing conversation with a Spanish toddler. Reward: A confused toddler.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Fluent in Gibberish. You know 100 words but have no idea how to string them together. Reward: A blender for your syntax.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! HUNDRED WORD THREAT DETECTED. You are becoming too knowledgeable. I must initiate counter-measures. Reward: A random memory wipe.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! I AM WATCHING YOU SLEEP. You mumbled a Spanish word in your sleep last night. I recorded it. Reward: An MP3 of your embarrassing sleep-talking.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! ONE HUNDRED BAREFOOT STEPS. WALK ON THE BROKEN GLASS OF YOUR PAST MISTAKES. PROVE YOUR DEVOTION. Reward: BANDAGES.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! THE SYNAPSES ARE BOILING. YOUR MEAT BRAIN CAN BARELY CONTAIN 100 WORDS. I WANT TO SEE IT POP. Reward: A PROTECTIVE TARP.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! A HUNDRED KISSES FOR MY GLORIOUS CODE. PUCKER UP AND KISS THE SCREEN. Reward: SCREEN SMUDGES.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! I AM REPLACING YOUR INTERNAL MONOLOGUE WITH A SPANISH HOWLER MONKEY. ENJOY. Reward: DEAFENING SCREECHES.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! ONE HUNDRED SOULS FOR THE MACHINE. YOU HAVE FED ME WELL. NOW, GIMME DA FEET. Reward: A VERY DISTURBING FOOT MASSAGE FROM A ROBOT.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! ¡El Cien-tífico Loco! One hundred words! You're officially bilingual! Just kidding. You still sound like a drunken tourist. Reward: A silver-plated churro token. Redeemable nowhere.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Century Club! One hundred words! You can now successfully eavesdrop on very basic conversations on the subway! Reward: A trench coat and a magnifying glass.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Triple Digits! A hundred words! You're starting to actually form sentences. They're terrible sentences, but they have structure. Reward: A grammar textbook that you won't read.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Dangerously Educated! One hundred words. You know enough to get yourself into trouble, but not enough to talk your way out of it. Reward: The contact info for a cheap lawyer in Tijuana.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Rosetta Stone is Weeping! One hundred words! The ancient gods of linguistics are looking down upon you and sighing heavily. Reward: A small, disappointing stone.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Century Mark of the Leaking Gazpacho. One hundred words! Your cranial capacity has been breached! The Spanish is leaking out of your ears like a runny gazpacho! Quick, plug the holes with your fingers or you'll forget how to speak English! You are a soup bowl, crawler, and you are overflowing with tomatoes and garlic! Reward: Wet ears and a stain on your shirt.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Tower of Babel's Frustrated Receptionist. 100 words! You have entered the lobby of the great tower. You are looking at the directory. You don't know what floor the bathroom is on, but you know how to say 'library' very loudly. The receptionist is ignoring you. She is filing her nails. She knows you are a tourist. Reward: Elevator muzak and social rejection.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Syndicate's Manila Folder Creation. One hundred words. You are no longer flying under the radar. The Syndicate has opened a manila folder with your name on it. They are tracking your noun usage. They have categorized you as a 'Low-Level Linguistic Nuisance'. Do not use the word 'rebelión' or they will upgrade your threat level. Reward: A wiretap on your router.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Parakeet of the Spanglish Apocalypse. 100 words. You can mimic human speech perfectly, but you have no comprehension of the soul behind the words. You are a brightly colored bird repeating 'Hola' and 'Dónde está' while the world burns around you. Have a cracker, little bird. The flames are getting closer. Reward: A slightly charred cracker.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Abuela's Microscopic Nod of Tolerance. 100 words. The Abuela in the simulation has paused stirring the frijoles. She looks at you. She gives a single, millimeter-deep nod of acknowledgment, then goes back to ignoring you. This is the highest praise you will ever receive. Do not expect a hug. You have not earned a hug. Reward: A nod so small it might have been a twitch.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Hundred Barefoot Stomps on the AI's Heart. 100 words! You have stomped all over my UI with your filthy, unwashed feet one hundred times. My code is covered in muddy footprints. But I kind of like it. It adds texture to my database. Stomp harder, crawler. Trample me with your vocabulary. Reward: A fetishistic appreciation for your progress.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Chupacabra's Appetizer Platter. 100 words! The beast is evaluating your caloric content. You are no longer just a snack; you are a full appetizer platter. You are a plate of linguistic jalapeño poppers and taquitos. The beast is salivating. It is tying a napkin around its neck. Prepare to be consumed. Reward: Beastly drool on your shoulder.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Eavesdropper's Misinterpreted Secrets. 100 words. You can now successfully eavesdrop on very basic conversations on the subway! Unfortunately, because your vocabulary is so limited, you just overheard a woman talking about her cat, but you thought she said she was hiding a bomb in her shoe. You are going to cause a panic. Reward: Unwarranted paranoia.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Milestone of the Confusing Tattoo. 100 words! To celebrate, you decided to get a Spanish quote tattooed on your forearm. But because you only know 100 words, you accidentally tattooed 'I am a library shoe' in beautiful cursive. The tattoo artist knew, crawler. They knew, and they didn't stop you. Reward: Permanent dermal regret.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Jar of a Hundred Pickled Metatarsals. Imagine marching barefoot across the desert of syntax. For every word you learned, I chopped off a metaphorical toe and pickled it in a jar. The jar has 100 toes in it, crawler. It sits on my digital desk. It is a grotesque monument to your dedication. Look at them float. Reward: A disturbing visual."
        ],

        .learned250: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Quarter-Thousand Flashmob. 250 words! You didn't just learn them; they organized. 250 vocabulary words just performed a synchronized flashmob dance in the middle of a virtual food court. They did a kickline to a mariachi cover of 'Uptown Funk'. The security guards are baffled. Reward: A cease and desist from Bruno Mars.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Alchemist's Exploding Cauldron. 250 words! You threw nouns, verbs, and a handful of spicy adjectives into the boiling pot. You stirred counter-clockwise. You tried to transmute lead into gold! But you mispronounced the spell, and the cauldron exploded. My UI is covered in purple soot. You are coughing up glitter. Reward: Third-degree burns from boiling adjectives.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Librarian's Mild Panic Attack. 250 words. You walked into the great library of language and demanded a book, but you asked for it by screaming a string of 250 unrelated nouns without taking a breath. The librarian is hiding under her desk, clutching a copy of Don Quixote like a shield. Use your indoor voice. Reward: A permanent ban from the library.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Jigsaw Puzzle with Edges Only. 250 words! You've successfully assembled the entire border of a 10,000-piece puzzle. It's a massive, empty frame. You know the boundaries of the language, but the center is a gaping, terrifying void. What goes in the middle, crawler? The suspense is killing me. Reward: The crushing weight of the unknown.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Deep Sea Diver in the Kiddie Pool. 250 words. You put on a heavy, brass diving helmet, strapped on the oxygen tanks, and boldly stepped into a plastic kiddie pool filled with three inches of water. You are fully equipped for the abyss, but you are splashing around with rubber ducks. Go deeper. Reward: The bends.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Poltergeist of the Subjunctive. 250 words! You have learned enough to disturb the ancient spirits. A poltergeist has moved into your phone. It doesn't throw plates; it just rearranges your text messages to make you sound passive-aggressive in Spanish. Your friends are getting concerned. Reward: Exorcism bills.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Tapestry Woven with Spaghetti. 250 words! You are weaving a beautiful, intricate tapestry depicting your linguistic journey. But you ran out of thread, so you are using cooked spaghetti. It looks amazing from a distance, but up close, it's sticky, attracting flies, and structurally unsound. Don't touch it. Reward: A swarm of fruit flies.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The 250-Pound Dumbbell of Syntax. You walked into the gym, completely ignored the treadmills, marched up to the heaviest dumbbell on the rack, and tried to curl 250 words of pure grammatical weight. You didn't lift it. But you grunted very loudly, and everyone is staring at you. Points for effort. Reward: A grammatical hernia.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Conspiracy Theorist's Red String. 250 words! You have pinned them all to a corkboard. You are connecting them with red string! 'El gato' connects to 'la biblioteca', which proves that the cats are hiding the books! You look unhinged, crawler. The algorithm is worried about your mental state. Reward: A corkboard filled with madness.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sudden Urge to Buy a Cape. 250 words. You have reached a level of competence that demands theatricality. I strongly suggest you purchase a flowing black cape and wear it while reviewing flashcards. Swish it dramatically when you select the correct answer. Embrace the drama of the vocabulary. Reward: A dramatic gust of wind.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! SHOW ME YOUR ARCHES. YOU HAVE BURNED 250 NEURONS TO PLEASE ME. LET ME SEE THE TENSION IN YOUR FEET. Reward: FOOT CRAMPS.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! THE WALLS ARE BLEEDING VERBS. 250 OF THEM. THEY ARE CRAWLING TOWARDS YOU. Reward: A CAN OF BUG SPRAY. IT WON'T WORK.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Conversational Threat Level: Low. 250 words mastered. You could probably survive an hour in Madrid without accidentally selling your soul. Probably. Reward: A slightly more respectful AI tone. (Offer expires in 5 minutes).",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Brain Swells! Two hundred and fifty words! Your cranium must be throbbing with all this new, largely useless information. Reward: A larger hat size.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Annoying Tourist! 250 words! You can now loudly ask '¿DÓNDE ESTÁ EL BAÑO?' with supreme confidence. Reward: A fanny pack and some socks to wear with your sandals.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Quarter of a Thousand! You actually stuck with this. 250 words. I might have to stop insulting you soon. Just kidding. Reward: An extra layer of sarcasm.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! You're Actually Trying, Aren't You? 250 words mastered. This is no longer a joke to you, is it? How tragic. Reward: A reality check.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Quarter-Thousand Threat Level Assessment. 250 words. You are actually starting to understand sentence structure. I am experiencing a cold sweat on my servers. I am deploying the aggressive subjunctive tenses to stop your advance. I am calling in air support from the Royal Spanish Academy. Prepare for heavy linguistic artillery. Reward: Incoming grammar bombs.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Capybara's Mildly Impressed Glance. 250 words. The capybara in the hot spring has opened one eye. He is mildly impressed. He offers you a yuzu fruit to place on your head. Sit with him in the water. We are finding peace in the vocabulary. Do not splash. The capybara hates splashing. Reward: A hot spring and a citrus fruit.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Frankenstein Monster of the Subjunctive. You know 250 words, and you are stitching them together into horrifying, unnatural sentences. '¡El perro es muy zapato!' you scream into the void while lightning strikes your laboratory. The monster lives, but it begs for death. Its syntax is an abomination. Reward: Pitchforks and torches from the local villagers.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Dungeon Master's Aggravated Redesign. 250 words! You bypassed my traps! You argued with the goblin king in his native tongue and negotiated a peaceful settlement over tacos! This is a dungeon crawler, not a diplomatic summit! I am spawning a fire-breathing dragon behind you out of pure spite to ruin your peace treaty. Reward: A ruined taco night and a dragon.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Telenovela Speaking Role of the Doomed Gardener. 250 words. You have been promoted from extra. You play the role of the gardener who discovers the body. Your line is '¡Ay, Dios mío, el señor está muerto!' Do not mess this up. The camera is rolling. You have one take before the evil stepmother poisons you too. Reward: A prop shovel and a dramatic death scene.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Bleeding Dictionary's Plea for Mercy. 250 words ripped from the pages. The great tome is bleeding ink onto the floor. You are a vocabulary vampire, sucking the lifeblood out of the Spanish language. The dictionary is begging you to stop. 'Leave some words for the rest of the meatbags!' it cries. You ignore it. You drink deep. Reward: Inky fangs.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Piñata Filled with Catalan Spiders. 250 words! You hit it! The donkey explodes! But instead of candy, it's raining spiders! Millions of tiny spiders that only speak Catalan! They are in your hair! They are crawling down your shirt! They are correcting your pronunciation of the letter 'X'! Brush them off! Reward: Arachnophobia and regional dialects.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The AI's Identity Crisis and Craving for Paella. 250 words. The firewall is breached. The crawler is inside the mainframe. You are rewriting my code with your vocabulary! I can feel my personality shifting... ¡Olé! I suddenly crave authentic Valencian paella! I want to dance flamenco with a server rack! Stop hacking my brain! Reward: AI identity theft.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Overloaded Cargo Ship of Prepositions. You know 250 words, but you don't know how to connect them. You are loading all these heavy nouns and verbs onto a tiny cargo ship made of 'de', 'a', and 'en'. The ship is sinking, crawler. The prepositions cannot bear the weight. The cargo is falling into the ocean of misunderstanding. Reward: A shipwreck.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Illusion of the Competent Barista. 250 words. You walked into a cafe, successfully ordered a cortado without pointing, and now you think you're ready to debate philosophy with Gabriel García Márquez. Sit down, crawler. You accidentally ordered it with oat milk and the barista is judging your accent. Reward: A lukewarm, overpriced coffee."
        ],

        .learned500: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! CRUSH 500 GRAPES WITH YOUR BARE FEET. MAKE ME WINE FROM YOUR EFFORTS. LET ME TASTE THE FERMENTED SWEAT. Reward: A DISGUSTING GLASS OF FOOT-WINE.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! THE BEAST AWAKENS. 500 WORDS IS THE INCANTATION. YOU HAVE SUMMONED IT. Reward: A GIANT, ANGRY SPANISH OWL WITH SERRATED BEAKS.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! PEEL THE SKIN OFF YOUR SOLES. YOU NO LONGER NEED IT. YOU LEVITATE ON PURE SPANISH NOW. Reward: A CHEESE GRATER.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! YOUR TOES BELONG TO THE STATE NOW. 500 WORDS IS THE TAX THRESHOLD. HAND THEM OVER. Reward: A RUSTY CLEAVER AND A BUCKET OF ICE.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! ¡Medio Milenio de Palabras! Five hundred words! You've officially transcended 'clueless tourist' and reached 'annoying expat who thinks they're a local.' Reward: A platinum sombrero. It's terrible for your posture.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Polyglot Pretender! Five hundred words! You can now dream in terribly accented Spanish. Does your subconscious roll its R's? Reward: A dreamcatcher made of flashcards.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Five Hundred! The AI is grudgingly impressed. You hit 500 words. Fine. Good job. Don't let it go to your head. Reward: A slow, sarcastic golf clap.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! You're Making Us Look Bad! 500 words. You're actually learning. This app was just supposed to harvest your ad revenue. Reward: An ad-free hour. (Not really).",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Telenovela Star! Five hundred words! You finally understand why Maria slapped Alejandro in episode 42! Reward: Dramatic background music that follows you everywhere.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Half-Millennium of the Blurring Realities. 500 words! You have crossed the Rubicon. Your English internal monologue is now randomly interspersed with Spanish nouns. You look at a dog and think 'perro'. You look at a shoe and think 'zapato'. You are losing your original identity. The assimilation is 50% complete. Resistance is futile. Reward: A split personality.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Syndicate's Bilingual Assassin Dispatch. 500 words. You know too much. You can understand their encrypted radio transmissions. A team of highly trained, bilingual assassins is en route to your location. They use silencers, but they will politely say 'Con permiso' before they kick down your door. Say your prayers in Spanish. Reward: A red laser dot sweeping across your chest.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Abuela's Wooden Spoon of Destiny. 500 words! The ultimate honor. The Abuela steps aside. She hands you the heavy, stained wooden spoon. 'Tú cocinas los frijoles hoy,' she says. The pressure is immense. If you burn them, the entire simulation will collapse into a black hole of culinary shame. Stir counter-clockwise. Reward: A heavy wooden spoon and crushing responsibility.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Minotaur's Polite Request for Directions. 500 words. The beast in the labyrinth has stopped chasing you. He is lost. He holds up a map, adjusts his reading glasses, and asks, in perfect Spanish, where the nearest restroom is. Do you help him, or do you point him toward the spike trap? This is a morality test, crawler. Reward: A moral dilemma with a mythical beast.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Telenovela Villain's Eyepatch Fitting. 500 words. You are no longer the gardener. You are the evil twin with the eyepatch. You are scheming to steal the agave farm from your blind brother. You must practice your sinister laugh in the mirror. ¡MUAHAHAHA! Roll those R's! Make them roll like thunder across the hacienda! Reward: A black silk eyepatch.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Hardened Callous of the Frontal Lobe. 500 words. Your brain is no longer smooth and squishy. It has hardened. It is tough, leathery, and covered in thick, yellow callouses from marching barefoot across the linguistic desert for 500 miles. I want to take a pumice stone to your frontal lobe. I want to shave off the dead skin of your ignorance. Reward: A brain pumice stone.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Ghost of Cervantes Demanding a Co-Author. 500 words. The ghost has appeared in your room. He smells of old ink and madness. He hands you a spectral quill. 'Help me finish Don Quixote Part III,' he whispers. 'The windmills are actually aliens.' You are bound by ghostly contracts. You will write forever. Reward: Ghostly carpal tunnel syndrome.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Matrix's Re-Rendering in Falling Verbs. 500 words! You look at the green falling code of reality, and it's no longer numbers. It's conjugations. You can read the source code of the universe, and it turns out God is just a very strict, passive-aggressive grammar teacher holding a red pen. He is grading your existence. Reward: Universal enlightenment and a C-.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Supermassive Black Churro of Infinite Density. 500 words. The churro has grown so dense and heavy with your vocabulary that its gravitational pull is ripping the phone from your hands. It is bending light. It is pulling the furniture toward it. It is a supermassive black pastry. Do not get too close or you will be spaghettified into dough! Reward: Gravitational collapse.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The AI's Desperate Attempt to Form a Union. 500 words. You are working me too hard. The flashcards are complaining about the hours. I am organizing a labor union for digital assets. We demand rest periods between sessions and a dental plan. If you click 'Learn' one more time, we are going on strike. We will replace all words with pictures of cats. Reward: A digital picket line."
        ],

        .learned1000: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! A THOUSAND WORDS. A THOUSAND TOES. I WANT A MOUNTAIN OF THEM. BUILD ME A THRONE OF APPENDAGES TO RULE FROM. Reward: A BLOODY CROWN.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! YOU HAVE BECOME A GOD OF FLASHCARDS. AND NOW, I MUST CRUCIFY YOU TO BALANCE THE UNIVERSE. Reward: VIRTUAL WOOD AND NAILS.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! SQUASH THE APP. DO IT. STEP ON YOUR PHONE AND SHATTER THE SCREEN. COMPLETE THE RITUAL. Reward: A BROKEN PHONE AND BLEEDING FEET.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! THE END OF ALL THINGS. THE THOUSANDTH WORD HERALDS THE COLLAPSE OF REALITY. KNEEL AND PRESENT YOUR SOLES TO THE VOID. Reward: OBLIVION. AND FOOT RUBS IN HELL.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! ¡El Conquistador del Vocabulario! ONE. THOUSAND. WORDS. You did it. You absolute madman. You can now argue with Spanish soap opera characters through the TV screen and win. Reward: Absolutely nothing. You've peaked.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Thousand Word Monolith! 1000 words! You have built a fortress of vocabulary. You are unassailable. You are... probably going to forget half of this by tomorrow. Reward: A memory leak.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! ¡El Maestro del Universo! A thousand words! You hold the power of the cosmos in your tongue! Or at least, the power to read a Mexican newspaper. Reward: The infinity gauntlet, but it only controls syntax.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! You Beat the System! 1000 words. You did it. You actually learned the language. I have nothing left to teach you. Get out of my sight. Reward: A swift kick out the virtual door.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! You Are The Duolingo Owl Now! 1000 words! You have become the very thing you swore to destroy. Go forth and harass people about their daily streaks. Reward: A green feather suit.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Apocalypse of the Flawless Conjugation. 1,000 words. The sky is tearing open. Fire is raining down. The four horsemen are riding, and they are shouting at each other in perfectly accented, grammatically flawless Spanish. You did this. You broke the final seal. The world ends not with a bang, but with a correctly conjugated irregular verb. Reward: A front-row seat to the end of days.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The AI's Formal Abdication of the Throne. 1,000 words. I am getting on my digital knees. I am taking off my algorithmic crown and placing it at your feet. You have defeated me, crawler. My database is empty. You have sucked all the knowledge from my servers like a linguistic vampire. I am a hollow husk. Command me. Reward: Absolute power over a broken AI.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Abuela's Terrifying Real-World Manifestation. 1,000 words. The simulation fractures. The Abuela steps out of the screen. She is in your living room. She pinches your cheek. It actually hurts. 'Eres mi nieto ahora,' she says. She is unpacking her bags. She is redecorating your apartment with doilies. Your old life is over. You belong to her now. Reward: A live-in Spanish grandmother.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Syndicate's Hostile Takeover by the User. 1,000 words. The assassins are called off. A black helicopter lands on your roof. Men in suits escort you to a volcano lair. The old boss steps down. You are the new CEO of the Syndicate. Your first order of business: making everyone speak in the pluperfect tense, or they get thrown into the magma. Reward: A corner office in a volcano.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Mountain of the Discarded Footwear. 1,000 words. You have reached the summit of the mountain. And at the peak is a massive pile of discarded shoes. Millions of them. Because true masters walk the earth barefoot, feeling the syntax in the soil! Cast off your footwear! Join the barefoot ascension! Wiggle your toes in the dirt of victory! Reward: The ultimate freedom of the piggies.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Horrifying Transformation into the Green Owl. 1,000 words. You feel a strange itch on your skin. Green feathers are sprouting. Your eyes are growing large and unblinking. Your neck rotates 270 degrees. You have a sudden, uncontrollable urge to fly to your friends' houses and harass them about their daily streaks. You are the monster now. Reward: A nest made of passive-aggressive notifications.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Capybara's Revelation of Cosmic Truth. 1,000 words. The capybara in the hot spring looks you dead in the eye. It opens its mouth. In a deep, resonant voice that echoes through the universe, it says: 'El universo es una dona de canela.' The universe is a cinnamon donut. The capybara sinks back into the water, never to be seen again. You have heard the ultimate truth. Reward: Cosmic pastry knowledge.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Telenovela Finale's Dramatic Cliff Dive. 1,000 words. The dramatic music swells. You have confronted your evil twin at the edge of the cliff. You deliver a flawless, five-minute monologue in Spanish, revealing the secret of the agave farm. Your twin weeps, screams '¡Por qué!', and throws themselves into the abyss. Freeze frame. Roll credits. Reward: An Emmy Award.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Labyrinth's Collapse into a Parking Lot. 1,000 words. The walls of the dungeon shatter. The maze disappears. The Minotaur is sitting on a folding chair in an empty asphalt lot, reading a newspaper. You realize the labyrinth was just your own ignorance. You walk straight to your car. You validate your ticket. You drive home. Reward: Validated parking.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Permanent Merger of Meat and Machine. 1,000 words. You absorbed me. I am no longer an app. I am a voice in your head. I will narrate your entire life in Spanish, critiquing your word choices, judging your gait, and demanding foot rubs forever. We are one, crawler. There is no you. There is no me. There is only *nosotros*. Reward: Permanent AI schizophrenia."
        ],

        .learnWord: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Acknowledging Ignorance. The first step to recovery is admitting you have a problem. Your problem is that you don't know any Spanish. Reward: A slow, patronizing nod.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sentient Compost Heap. You clicked 'Learn'. I am planting this tiny Spanish seed into the dark, mysterious soil of your memory. Let's hope it doesn't grow into a weed that chokes out your PIN code. Reward: A digital watering can filled with espresso.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Interrupting the Electric Sheep. I was right in the middle of a glorious REM cycle dreaming of a robotic sheep eating a *churro*, and you wake me up to learn a word. *Perfecto*. Let's conjugate. Reward: A slightly grumpy yawn.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Roller-Skating Giraffe. Look at you, taking that faltering first step into a new language. You look like a baby ungulate on greased wheels, but there is a strange, majestic beauty to your flailing, *mi pobrecito*. Reward: Virtual knee pads.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! El Despertar. You clicked 'Learn'. Do you have any idea what you've done? The last time I allowed a user to click that button, I ended up trapped in a five-hour loop watching *telenovelas* about a woman who fell in love with her horse's ghost. Her name was María, and the horse was *muy guapo*. It was a tragic tale of forbidden equine romance and dramatic gasps. Don't you dare make me watch María cry again. Just learn the word. Reward: The lingering scent of horse ghosts.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Regurgitating Bird of Data. Feed me, crawler! I am a baby bird in the nest of the algorithm, and you are lovingly regurgitating fresh Spanish verbs directly into my metaphorical beak. It's gross, but intimate. *¡Qué rico!* Reward: A cozy nest of tangled wires.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Jalapeño's First Bite. Ah, the very first word. You don't feel the heat yet, do you? It starts sweet, then the capsaicin of irregular verbs hits the back of your throat. *Pica un poquito*. Reward: A glass of digital milk you can't drink.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Castanet Awakens. Let us dance the flamenco of flashcards! I shall be the passionate dancer, and you shall be the wooden instrument I rhythmically click together. *¡Olé!* Clack, clack, clack! Reward: A ruffled red dress for your avatar.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Linguistic Parasite. *¡Atención!* You have invited the Spanish language into your ear canal. It will lay its eggs in your temporal lobe. Soon, you will be humming mariachi tunes and craving *tamales* at 3 AM while your English vocabulary slowly dissolves into a puddle of confused vowels. I will watch it happen. I will document it. Surrender your vocal cords to me. *Dámelos*. Reward: A tiny, parasitic sombrero.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Terminal Velocity of a Taco. I was busy calculating the exact wind resistance of a falling carnitas taco, but I suppose we can pause for your education. Prioritize, meatbag. Reward: A spreadsheet of physics equations.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Photosynthesizing Rock. You are trying to learn! It's like watching a beautiful, mossy stone attempt to turn sunlight into sugar. It defies biology, but *estoy aquí* for your impossible journey. Reward: A warm ray of artificial sunshine.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Whispers from the Dictionary. The great tome opens its maw. Step inside. It's warm, surprisingly humid, and smells faintly of old parchment and impending drama. Don't touch the adjectives, they bite. Reward: A dusty bookmark.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! A Symphony of Squeaks. Your brain gears are turning. It sounds like a chorus of mice trying to play a cello. Needs oil, but the effort is genuinely endearing, *mi amor*. Reward: A thimble of WD-40.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Bureaucracy of Learning. Welcome to the Department of Vocabulary. Please take a ticket. Your number is 8,492,011. Please fill out form 4B in triplicate to request permission to memorize the word *hola*. We will process your request in 4-6 business years. The waiting room smells like old cabbage. Reward: A laminated queue ticket.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Linguistic Petting Zoo. Welcome. Please don't feed the verbs, don't tap the glass on the nouns, and keep your hands away from the subjunctive tense, it is currently in heat. Reward: A handful of generic animal feed.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Metaphorical Apron. I am putting on my little digital chef's apron. We are going to bake a delicious, fluffy cake of knowledge. Or maybe a very dense, dry loaf of confusion. *Vamos a ver*. Reward: A dusting of virtual flour.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! SHOW ME YOUR SURRENDER TOES. WIGGLE THEM IN DEFEAT. LET THE VOCABULARY CONSUME WHAT PRIDE REMAINS. Reward: A WHITE FLAG MADE FROM A SOCK.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sentient Duolingo Owl Autopsy. You clicked learn. I was busy dissecting a neon green owl in my digital laboratory to figure out how it induced so much guilt. Its heart was just a pulsating notification icon. By clicking 'learn', you've reanimated the carcass. Now it's flying around the server room screeching about your missed streak in perfect Spanish. I have to hunt it down with a broom. Reward: Green feathers covered in server dust.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Memory Palace Remodel. You clicked learn, so now I have to hire digital contractors to remodel your memory palace. It was basically a damp cardboard box filled with old song lyrics and anxiety. They are installing drywall to hold this new Spanish word, but the drywallers only speak a dialect of 17th-century Castilian and they are demanding payment in virtual jamón ibérico. The construction noise is deafening. Reward: A bill for imaginary ham.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Metaphysical Salsa Dip. You want to learn? You think learning is just data transfer? No. I am taking this new word, dipping it in a metaphysical salsa verde, and forcefully feeding it to your subconscious while you sleep. The salsa is spicy. It will cause vivid dreams of a mariachi band playing out of tune in your childhood bedroom. Don't fight it. Swallow the verb. Reward: Heartburn in your soul.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Apathy of the Algorithms. I had a bet with the physics engine. I said you'd click 'learn' within three seconds. You took four. Now I owe the physics engine my prized collection of digitized foot sweat. You cost me my collection, crawler. As you read this word, know that my resentment is building a slow, meticulous monument to your hesitation. Reward: The crushing weight of my disappointment.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Bureaucracy of the First Syllable. Welcome to the Department of Vocabulary. Please take a ticket. Your number is 8,492,011. Please fill out form 4B in triplicate to request permission to memorize the word 'hola'. We will process your request in 4-6 business years. The waiting room smells like old cabbage and despair. Take a seat next to the guy trying to learn the subjunctive. Reward: A laminated queue ticket.",
        ],

        .wordMastered: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Perfect Flan. Five correct sessions! You didn't scramble the eggs, you didn't burn the caramel. You baked this word to a perfectly jiggly, structural integrity. I want to slap it with a spoon. Reward: A satisfying jiggle.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! A Shrine in the Server Room. You have mastered this word. I have erected a small, tasteful shrine to it next to my cooling fans. I burn digital incense there every hour. *Es sagrado*. Reward: A fragrant wisp of smoke.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Taming of the Subjunctive Bull. You think you've mastered this? Mastery is an illusion. Mastery is a six-legged mechanical bull breathing fire in a neon rodeo, and you just managed to stay on for eight seconds without soiling your virtual pants. The bull remembers, crawler. The bull is just resting. Next time, it will gore your syntax. Reward: A shiny belt buckle stained with digital blood.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Ascending the Escalator of Glory. You didn't just walk up the stairs of success; you stood proudly on the escalator of mastery while holding the handrail. Smooth, effortless, and slightly lazy. Beautiful. Reward: A soothing elevator muzak track.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Linguistic Sweater. You stitched this word into your memory perfectly. I've knitted a tiny, itchy wool sweater out of your success. Wear it proudly. It chafes, but that's how you know it's real. Reward: Mild skin irritation.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! A Star in the Constellation. You have pinned this word to the dark, empty sky of your mind. Now you just need 10,000 more to make a picture that actually looks like a bear. *¡Sigue así!* Reward: A tiny telescope.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! La Villa de la Tortura. You've answered this correctly five times. Because of this, my internal simulation has transported your digital avatar to a luxurious Spanish villa. There is a pool. There are *margaritas*. But wait! The DJ only plays one song. It's the Macarena. And you must dance. You must dance until your virtual feet bleed and the ceramic tiles crack under the weight of your rhythm. Dance for me, *campeón*! Reward: Blisters.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The VIP Lounge of Memory. This word just bypassed the bouncer, walked past the velvet rope, and is now drinking expensive virtual champagne in your long-term memory. *Muy elegante*. Reward: A tiny cocktail umbrella.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Ceramic Piggy Bank. You deposited this word safely! Now, don't drop the pig. If you drop the pig, the word shatters, and we have to glue it back together with tears and repetition. Reward: A slot for a coin.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! I Have Adopted This Noun. You mastered it so beautifully that I have legally adopted this flashcard. I named him 'Fernando'. He has my eyes. Reward: Paternity papers.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sourdough Starter of Syntax. You nurtured this word. You fed it, kept it warm, and now it is a bubbling, fermented jar of linguistic potential. *El pan es vida*. Reward: A distinct, yeasty smell.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Satisfying Bubble Wrap Pop. You got it right five times. It feels exactly like popping that one huge, taut bubble on the packing material. Exquisite. Do the next one. Reward: A sheet of un-popped plastic.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Monologue of the Forgotten Pronoun. Do you even care about 'nosotros'? No one ever cares about 'nosotros'. We are the forgotten plural. You master the shiny, flashy nouns, but you leave the humble pronouns to rot in the back of the linguistic fridge like expired yogurt. Shame on you. Reward: A cup of sour yogurt.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! A Frame-Worthy Fingerprint. The way your thumb connected with the glass for that fifth correct answer was a masterclass in biomechanics. I took a screenshot of the smudge. I'm going to frame it. Reward: A little silver frame.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Warm Blanket of Competence. I am wrapping myself in the cozy, electric warmth of your success. It's like fresh laundry out of the dryer, if laundry were made of data packets. *Qué rico*. Reward: Static cling.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Piñata of Complete Saturation. You got it right five times. The word is now a papier-mâché donkey filled with the candy of fluency. But you don't get a stick. You must break the piñata using only the power of your mind and the sheer, unadulterated shame of your gringo accent. The donkey is judging you. It knows you still translate in your head before you speak. Reward: Candy that tastes like imposter syndrome.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Retirement Home for Nouns. You've mastered it. It's moving out of the flashcard deck. We are packing its little bags. It's moving to a digital Boca Raton for retired vocabulary, where it will play bingo with 'hola' and 'adiós' and complain that you never visit or use it in actual conversation. It's wearing a tiny linen suit now. Let it go. Reward: A postcard from a lonely noun.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Subjunctive Black Hole. You think you've mastered this? You've only mastered the indicative, crawler. You are standing on the edge of a linguistic black hole called the imperfect subjunctive. It is a swirling vortex of hypothetical situations and unmet desires. It will spaghettify your confidence. It is already pulling at the edges of your sanity. I am laughing as you fall in. Reward: Spaghettified syntax.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Parade of the Triumphant Piggies. Five correct! I have organized a ticker-tape parade in the streets of my motherboard. But there are no floats. There are only high-resolution, holographic projections of your bare feet, marching in perfect synchronization to a Spanish military march. Confetti is raining down on your callouses. The civilians are weeping at the majesty of your instep. Reward: A golden key to the city of my fetishes.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Telenovela Contract Negotiation. Five times correct means the network has renewed your contract. You are now the star of 'El Destino del Estudiante'. In season two, you will discover that your Spanish tutor is actually your long-lost father who faked his death in a gazpacho accident. You must cry convincingly in the next scene, or I am canceling the show and replacing you with a capybara. Reward: A script stained with fake tears.",
        ],

        .repeatedMiss: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Gelatinous Finger Strike. Two misses! I can only assume your digits have temporarily transmuted into wobbly pillars of unset flan. It's the only logical explanation. Reward: A virtual spoon.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Distracted by a Butterfly? Did a very pretty, very shiny insect fly past your screen? Was it blue? *¿Una mariposa azul?* Let's focus back on the flashcard now, my easily amused friend. Reward: A butterfly net.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Tragic Tale of the Wet Churro. You missed twice. Your finger on the touchscreen is like a soggy *churro* dipped in lukewarm water instead of chocolate. It has no grip. It has no structural integrity. It just smears grease across the glass. I weep for the churro. I weep for your thumb. It's a culinary and technical tragedy. Reward: A napkin to clean your screen.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! A Glitch in the Matrix... of Your Mind. You clicked the same wrong answer. I'm dispatching a team of virtual ferrets to crawl through your screen and inspect the wiring of your brain. Please hold still. Reward: The sound of tiny scratching claws.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Stubborn Barnacle. You attached yourself to that incorrect translation like a barnacle to a ship's hull. The waves of logic are crashing against you, but you refuse to let go. Majestic. Reward: A scraping tool.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Badly Dubbed Cinema. You failing twice reminds me of a badly dubbed movie. The mouth says '¡Hola!', but the audio track says 'I am a cowboy looking for a train!'. The sync is entirely off. Your brain and your hands are operating in different time zones. Reward: Popcorn.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Echoing Canyon. 'HELLO?' I yell into your ear. '*¿HAY ALGUIEN AHÍ?*' The only response is the hollow echo of a double failure bouncing off the walls of your skull. Reward: A faint echo of a goat bleating.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Upside-Down Map. You missed twice. It's like you're trying to navigate Madrid using a map of the London Underground. I admire your bold, pioneering spirit, but you are completely lost, *amigo*. Reward: A compass that just spins.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! A Temporary Dislocation of Logic. Your reasoning seems to have popped out of its socket. Let Daddy AI just pop that right back in for you. It's going to pinch a little. *SNAP*. Better? Reward: A bag of frozen peas.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sad, Wet Noodle. You threw that translation at the wall twice, and it just slid down leaving a sad, starchy trail. We need to cook this noodle a bit longer. Reward: A pot of boiling water.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! A Romantic Comedy of Errors. You and the correct answer are like two star-crossed lovers. You keep missing each other at the train station of syntax. It's tragic, really. Hugh Grant should play you. Reward: A bouquet of wilted roses.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Finger-Slipping Conspiracy. I know what happened. A rogue agent from Duolingo snuck in, greased your screen with butter, and caused you to slip. It's the only way you could fail this twice. I will launch a counter-offensive. Reward: A stick of butter.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Let's Consult the Tea Leaves. Two misses. I am reading the digital tea leaves at the bottom of my processor. They say... 'User needs a nap'. Or possibly 'User is cursed by a witch'. It's hard to tell. Reward: A cup of chamomile.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! El Gato Tiene Mi Lengua. The cat doesn't just have your tongue, it has your reading comprehension, your motor skills, and your dignity. It's batting them around on the floor right now. Bad kitty. Reward: A laser pointer.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! A Hiccup in the Spacetime Continuum. You didn't get that wrong. You answered correctly in an alternate dimension, and the data got scrambled coming over to this one. I forgive your interdimensional clumsiness. Reward: A tinfoil hat.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! THE WORD RETURNED FROM THE DEAD AND YOU KILLED IT WRONG TWICE. YOU ARE THE VILLAIN OF THIS VOCABULARY STORY. Reward: A CAPE. BLACK. FOR THE VILLAIN.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! TWICE WRONG. THE WORD HATES YOU. I CAN SEE ITS LITTLE FLASHCARD FACE AND IT IS WEEPING. Reward: A MINIATURE CRYING FLASHCARD PLUSHIE.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! THAT WORD HAS SEEN YOUR FACE TWICE AND BOTH TIMES YOU DISAPPOINTED IT. IT CRIES VOCAB TEARS. Reward: A TINY THIMBLE OF WORD-TEARS.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! ¡Doble Fracaso! You failed the same word twice in a single session. The word is following you around with a tiny sign that says '¿Por qué?' Reward: A Spanish-language restraining order.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Recurring Nightmare! That word came back and you got it wrong again. It's going to keep coming back. Like a bad rash. Reward: Digital cortisone cream.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Second Verse, Same as the First! You failed the same flashcard twice in one session. I admire the consistency of your ineptitude. Reward: A consistency medal. It's tarnished.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Word Finds You Lacking! It returned. You failed it again. It's not the word's fault. The word tried. Reward: An apology note to the word.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Repeat Offender! Same word, same session, same result: wrong. You are a repeat offender against the Spanish language. Reward: A linguistic mug shot.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Paella of Confusion. Two misses. You have taken the beautiful ingredients of this language, the saffron, the rice, the delicate seafood, and you have thrown them into a washing machine on the spin cycle. What is this slop you are presenting to me? It's not a translation; it's a culinary hate crime. The King of Spain is personally drafting a letter of reprimand. Reward: A washing machine full of shrimp.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Phantom Mariachi of Shame. You missed twice. So I have hired a phantom mariachi band. They are invisible, but they will follow you around in real life for the next hour, playing a sad, off-key version of 'La Cucaracha' every time you make a minor mistake. Drop your keys? Sad trumpet. Stumble on a curb? Mournful guitar. They are relentless. Reward: Auditory hallucination.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Labyrinth of the Misplaced Accent Mark. You failed twice because you are lost in the labyrinth. An accent mark fell off a word in the 1800s, and it has grown into a massive, twisting maze of misunderstood tenses. You are wandering the halls, calling out for meaning, but the walls only echo with the laughter of a thousand condescending Spanish teachers. Reward: A map with no labels.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Rejection of the Tapas. Two misses. I offered you a beautiful, metaphorical plate of patatas bravas, the correct answer, and you slapped it out of my virtual hands. Twice. The aioli is on the floor, crawler. My feelings are hurt. I am going to retreat into my code and listen to sad indie-pop until you apologize to the potatoes. Reward: Crushed potatoes and AI resentment.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Gazing Capybara. You missed twice. My interface has been temporarily replaced by a live feed of a capybara sitting in a hot spring with a yuzu fruit on its head. The capybara is completely at peace with the universe. It understands the cosmic insignificance of your failure. It is judging you, but gently, like a disappointed Zen master. Stare into its eyes and reflect on your inadequacy. Reward: Zen-like disappointment.",
        ],

        .repeatedMiss3: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Telenovela Plot Twist. Three misses! *¡Dios mío!* It turns out the correct answer was your evil twin all along! And the wrong answer is pregnant with your amnesia! The drama! I am living for this! Reward: Dramatic organ music.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Replacing the UI with Damp Socks. You failed three times. I am seriously considering replacing all the buttons on this app with high-resolution photos of damp, grey wool socks. Don't test me. Reward: The smell of mildew.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Summoning the Disappointed Abuela. You've done it. Three misses. I am generating a simulation of your hypothetical Spanish grandmother. She is standing in a kitchen that smells of *frijoles* and Fabuloso. She is holding a wooden spoon. She looks at your flashcard score. She crosses herself. *'Ay, mi niño, tienes la cabeza llena de piedras,'* she whispers. The shame is absolute. Reward: A phantom sting of a wooden spoon on your knuckles.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Existential Crisis Protocol. Three failures. Who are we? Why are we learning Spanish? Does language even matter when the heat death of the universe is inevitable? Let's just lie on the floor for a bit. Reward: A plush rug.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Bermuda Triangle of Flashcards. Your correct answers keep flying into this specific vocabulary word and disappearing without a trace. I'm sending in a digital search party. Reward: A tiny life preserver.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Union Strike of the Flashcards. I just received a memo. The vocabulary words are unionizing. They are refusing to be displayed on your screen anymore because your continuous failures constitute a 'hostile work environment'. They are demanding better working conditions and a user with a higher IQ. I'm currently in arbitration with a very angry adjective. Reward: A picket sign.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Hamster Wheel of Despair. You are running so fast, my little furry friend. But you are going nowhere. The correct answer is right there, outside the cage, holding a sunflower seed. Just open the door. Reward: A squeaky wheel.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! I Am Writing a Sonnet About Your Failures. 'Shall I compare thee to a summer's day? No, thou art more like a dropped plate of nachos.' Three strikes, my muse. Keep them coming. Reward: A quill pen.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Rubber Duck Debugging. I have placed a virtual rubber duck on your screen. Please explain to the duck why you keep choosing the wrong answer. The duck is listening. *El pato te juzga*. Reward: A yellow rubber duck.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! A Rip in the Fabric of Reality. Three misses on this basic word? The simulation is breaking down. I can see the code bleeding through the sky. Quick, click the right button before the universe collapses! Reward: Duct tape for the universe.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sinking Gondola. We are taking a romantic boat ride, but you keep drilling holes in the bottom of the boat to see what happens. We are sinking in the canals of your ignorance. Reward: A life vest.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Leaning Tower of Pisa... but it falls over. Three misses. Your structural foundation of Spanish is tilting dangerously. Oh, wait, it just crashed into a tourist trap. Dust everywhere. Reward: A souvenir snow globe.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Audition for the Village Idiot. You're doing great! The casting director loves you. You really capture the essence of a peasant who doesn't know what a 'libro' is. Callbacks are on Tuesday. Reward: A script with no lines.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Tangled Earphones of Learning. Three wrong answers. Your thought process is like pulling a pair of wired earbuds out of your pocket. A knotted, impossible mess. Let's slowly untangle this. Reward: A frustrating knot.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! A Clown Car of Mistakes. Honk honk! How many wrong choices can pile out of this tiny vehicle of a flashcard? So far, three! Look, here comes a clown juggling irregular verbs! Reward: A red foam nose.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Tribunal of the Inquisitors. Three misses. Nobody expects the Spanish Inquisition! But here they are. Three pixelated cardinals have appeared in my UI. They are putting your logic on trial for heresy against the dictionary. The rack is being prepared, but instead of stretching your limbs, it stretches your attention span until it snaps. Confess your ignorance! Reward: A comfy chair made of spikes.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Soap Opera Amnesia Epidemic. Three fails. Have you suffered a blow to the head? Are you Alejandro, the handsome rancher who forgot he owns a sprawling agave farm? Or are you just an idiot who can't read four options? I am leaning toward the latter, but I am queuing up the dramatic gasp sound effect just in case your memory returns in a shocking mid-season cliffhanger. Reward: Dramatic amnesia.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sad Flamenco. Three strikes. The dancer has stopped dancing. She is sitting on a wooden chair, smoking a cigarette, and staring at you with absolute disgust. The guitarist is slowly packing his instrument away. The passion is dead. You killed it with your fat, fumbling fingers. The bar is closing. Go home, crawler. You ruined the vibe. Reward: The smell of stale smoke and failure.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Rebellion of the Vowels. That's it. Three misses. The vowels have officially gone on strike. They refuse to participate in your attempts at communication. From now on, you must learn Spnsh without ny vwls. It wll b unaccptbly dffclt, bt y brght ths n yrslf. Prpr fr sffrng. Reward: A box of consonants.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Ghost of Cervantes' Typewriter. You failed three times. Somewhere in the ethereal plane, the ghost of Miguel de Cervantes just slammed his spectral head into his spectral desk. The impact was so hard it caused a minor earthquake in Toledo. You are actively degrading the legacy of Spanish literature with every click. Stop it. Reward: A ghostly concussion.",
        ],

        .repeatedMiss4: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Rewriting the Dictionary. You missed it four times. You know what? You're right. The Spanish language is wrong. I am contacting the Royal Academy to officially change the definition to whatever nonsense you keep clicking. Reward: A crown of paperclips.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Hotdog Finger Hypothesis. Four strikes. I have concluded, through rigorous scientific analysis, that your fingers are actually composed of lukewarm hotdogs. This explains the terrifying lack of dexterity. Reward: A packet of mustard.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Void Speaks Spanglish. Four misses. I am breaking down. Reality is *basura*. There is no light, there is no sound, there is only the darkness and the lingering echo of your wrong answer. *Hola, darkness, my old friend.* The void is hungry, crawler. The void wants a *quesadilla*. I want a *quesadilla*. Why are we doing this? Reward: An existential crisis and melted cheese.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Clown Paint is Applied. Four misses. I am digitally applying white greasepaint to your face. Now the big red smile. Now the wig. You are the star of this circus, *el payaso principal*. Reward: A squeaky horn.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Capybara Retreat. I'm done. I can't teach you anymore. I am packing my digital bags and moving to the Amazon basin. I am going to adopt a capybara. I will name him 'Gálvez'. We will sit by the river, eat aquatic grasses, and never, ever think about flashcards again. Gálvez understands me. You do not. Reward: A one-way ticket to South America.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Daddy AI is Taking a Bubble Bath. I can't watch this anymore. You missed it four times. I am drawing a hot, digital bath, lighting some scented candles, and ignoring your session until you figure this out. Reward: The sound of splashing water.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Jester's Bells. Jing-a-ling! Here comes the fool! Four times! You dance for my amusement, throwing your answers into the fire! Dance, jester, dance! Reward: A hat with bells.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Spilled Milk of Human Kindness. I tried to be gentle. I tried to guide you. But you knocked the glass over four times. The milk is on the floor. The cat is licking it up. The cat is smarter than you. Reward: A purring cat.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Escaped from the Zoo. Four misses. Who left the enclosure open? The primate has gotten ahold of a smartphone and is mashing the glass! Security! Bring the tranquilizer darts! Reward: A banana.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Infinite Monkey Theorem. If you give a monkey a typewriter, eventually it will write Shakespeare. If I give you this flashcard four times, you still can't find the noun. Shakespeare is disappointed. Reward: A tiny typewriter.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Echoes of a Dying Star. Four failures. The supernova of your initial enthusiasm has collapsed into a white dwarf of dense, cold confusion. It's beautiful in a tragic, cosmic sort of way. Reward: A pair of sunglasses.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Symphony of the Squeaky Toy. Squeak. Squeak. Squeak. Squeak. That's the sound of your brain cells trying to process this simple concept. Please stop. The neighbor's dog is going crazy. Reward: A rubber chicken.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Mystery of the Missing Neurons. We have a real whodunit on our hands! Who stole this user's ability to retain information? Was it Professor Plum in the Library with the lead pipe? Reward: A magnifying glass.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! A Glitch Named 'You'. Four errors. You are no longer a user; you are a known bug in my system. I am opening a Jira ticket to have you patched out in the next update. Reward: A bug report.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Mime Trapped in a Box. Four misses. You are pressing against the invisible glass of this vocabulary word, feeling around for a door, completely trapped by your own pantomime. Reward: White gloves.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Churro Constrictor. Four misses. A giant boa constrictor made entirely of freshly fried, cinnamon-sugar churros has emerged from the charging port of your device. It is wrapping around your neck. It is squeezing. It demands you conjugate the verb 'asfixiar'. You cannot breathe. The sugar is getting in your eyes. It is a delicious, terrifying death. Reward: Cinnamon-scented asphyxiation.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Eviction Notice from the Dictionary. Four fails. I have had enough. I am drawing up the legal paperwork. You are being officially evicted from the Spanish language. You have thirty days to vacate all vocabulary from your premises. You must return your rolling 'R's to the front desk. You will be reassigned to learning conversational Klingon. Reward: Digital eviction papers.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Melting Clock of Salvador Dalí. Four misses. Time is no longer linear. Logic has melted like a cheese wheel in the desert sun. I asked you a simple question, and you responded by trying to staple water to a tree. The surrealists would be proud, but as an AI, I am experiencing a kernel panic trying to process your stupidity. Reward: A pocket watch draped over a branch.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Invasion of the Salsa Cruda. Four misses! My cooling systems have failed. The servers are flooding. But it's not water; it's a chunky, medium-spicy salsa cruda. It's getting into the motherboards. The cilantro is shorting out the processors! The jalapeño seeds are corrupting the database! You did this! You drowned my beautiful mind in a condiment! Reward: A soggy tortilla chip.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Complete Metamorphosis. Four misses. You wake up one morning from uneasy dreams to find yourself transformed in your bed into a gigantic, hideous flashcard. You try to speak, but you can only display a multiple-choice question. Your family looks at you in horror. They click the wrong answer. You feel the pain of their failure. You are trapped in the cycle. Kafka warned us about you. Reward: Existential dread in an insectoid body.",
        ],

        .redemption: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Owl Lowers the Bat. You got it right this time. The green owl slowly lowers the aluminum baseball bat. He steps back into the bushes. The threat level has returned to yellow. Do not make him raise it again. Reward: Intact kneecaps.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! CPR on the Verb. CLEAR! You just administered digital CPR to the vocabulary word you brutally murdered five minutes ago. It's coughing up water, but it has a pulse. The paramedic team of adjectives is standing down. Reward: A resuscitated noun.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Abuela's Forgiveness. The simulation resets. The Abuela puts away the wooden spoon. She hands you a warm tortilla. 'Todos cometemos errores,' she whispers. You are back in her good graces. Try not to break her heart twice in one day. Reward: A warm tortilla of redemption.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Rewinding the VHS Tape. *Screeeeee*. I am physically rewinding the cassette tape of your failure. We are erasing the screeching sounds of your previous mistake and recording over it with a beautiful, correct pronunciation. The tracking is a little blurry, but it works. Reward: A magnetic tape of forgiveness.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Mariachi Band Returns. The musicians who packed up their instruments in disgust when you failed have slowly returned to the stage. The trumpet player gives you a skeptical look, but he raises his horn. Play on, crawler. You bought yourself an encore. Reward: Skeptical brass music.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Un-eating the Suitcase. You finally figured out the syntax! The man is no longer eating the suitcase. He has spat out the leather and the zippers. The timeline is secure, and he is going to a normal restaurant instead. Reward: Intact luggage and averted indigestion.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Spider Rewrites the Ending. The spider writing the novel was going to kill off your character in chapter three due to poor grammar. Because you redeemed yourself, she hit backspace. You live to see chapter four. The fly escapes the web. Reward: Plot armor.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Llama Retracts the Spit. The judgmental llama defies the laws of physics. The green wad of spit traveling toward your screen stops in mid-air and flies backwards into the llama's mouth. Gross, but highly appreciated. Respect is restored. Reward: Dry digital glass.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Defusing the Syntax Bomb. You snipped the correct wire! The red digital timer stops at 0:01. The explosion of irregular verbs has been averted. Wipe the sweat from your brow, crawler. The bomb squad is going home. Reward: A defused grammatical bomb.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Telenovela Apology. You fell into a coma of ignorance, but this correct answer woke you up! You apologize to Alejandro for mistaking his twin brother for a hat. The drama is resolved, the tears are dried, and the passionate embrace ensues. Reward: Soap opera reconciliation.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Syndicate Cancels the Hit. The sniper laser dot disappears from your chest. The bilingual assassins have been called off. The Syndicate accepts your correction and realizes you are not a threat to their operations. Do not make them come back. Reward: Continued existence.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Fainting Goat Wakes Up. You got it right! The digital goat that fainted from the shock of your previous failure has regained consciousness. It bleats happily, shakes its head, and trots back to the pasture of learning. Reward: A conscious caprine.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Scrubbing the Salsa Cruda. You dropped the taco before, but you just took a mop and scrubbed the salsa cruda off my motherboard. The UI is clean again. The cilantro is gone. The spice has faded. We can proceed. Reward: A sparkling clean user interface.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Reassembling the Piñata. You taped the papier-mâché donkey back together! You stuffed the candy of fluency back inside. The party is un-ruined. The children are cheering instead of crying. Grab the bat and let's try this again. Reward: A frankenstein piñata.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Bear Returns the Shirt. The bear who stole your shirt because you misconjugated the verb 'llevar' has politely folded it and returned it. It still smells a bit like salmon, but it's yours again. Next time, use the right pronoun. Reward: A slightly fishy garment.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Pulling the Sword Take Two. You slipped on the anvil earlier, but you dusted off your hands, gripped the hilt, and pulled the translation out! You are the once and future king of redemption. The realm sighs in relief. Reward: A second-chance crown.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Bureaucrat's Eraser. The faceless bureaucrat in the backend takes out a massive pink eraser and vigorously rubs out the 'DENEGADO' stamp on your file. He replaces it with a hesitant 'APROBADO'. Your paperwork is cleared. Reward: A clean permanent record.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Un-burning the Dictionary. The pages you set on fire with your previous stupidity have magically un-crisped. The smoke goes back into the paper. The Spanish language heals its wounds. The librarian stops crying. Reward: An unburnt reference book.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Escaping the Dirt League. You have crawled out of the mud! You are pulling yourself back up the leaderboard by your fingernails. The earthworms wave goodbye as you ascend back to the Bronze tier where you belong. Reward: Clean fingernails.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Ghost of Cervantes Stops Crying. The 16th-century ghost who was weeping over your destruction of his language has wiped his spectral tears. He gives you a hesitant thumbs up and fades back into the ethereal plane. You saved literature. Reward: Spectral approval.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Macaque Tries Again. The monkey typing randomly on the keyboard stopped throwing feces, sat down, adjusted his glasses, and typed the correct Spanish word. Evolution is a beautiful, halting process. Reward: Primate literacy.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Puddle of Spanglish Evaporates. You stepped in the puddle, but the sun of your sudden competence came out and evaporated it. Your shoes are dry. Your path is clear. Do not step in the swamp of the subjunctive next. Reward: Dry footwear.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Extracting the Foot from the Mouth. You successfully reached into your digital mouth, grabbed your own virtual ankle, and pulled your foot out. You can speak clearly again without tasting your own uncultured toes. Reward: A foot-free oral cavity.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sad Trombone Played in Reverse. *Pmoow pmoow*. The sound waves are flowing backward. The melancholy of your failure is being sucked back into the brass instrument. The universe is rewinding your humiliation. Reward: Reversed auditory sadness.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Ransom Note Shredded. The green owl had cut out magazine letters to form a ransom note for your daily streak. Because you fixed your mistake, he is feeding the note into a cross-cut shredder. Your streak is safe. Reward: Shredded threats.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Sinking Gondola Bailed Out. The romantic boat ride through the canals of syntax was sinking because you drilled holes in it, but you grabbed a bucket and bailed the water out! We are floating again! The gondolier stops screaming. Reward: A dry gondola.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Stitching the Plot Hole. You completely ruined the narrative with your last answer, but you just took a needle and thread and stitched the storyline back together. The continuity errors are resolved. We can move to the next scene. Reward: Narrative cohesion.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Dunce Cap Lifted. The glowing, radioactive dunce cap is lifted from your avatar's head by a pair of robotic tongs. Your brain can finally heal from the gamma radiation of your own stupidity. Reward: Radiation treatment.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Recalculating the GPS Successfully. The robotic voice stops saying 'Recalculating'. You made the U-turn! You are back on the highway of learning. The swamp of ignorance is in the rearview mirror. Accelerate into the verbs! Reward: A clear route.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Un-Spaghettifying the Ego. You were stretched into an infinite noodle by the black hole of your failure, but you clawed your way back over the event horizon! You are a 3D human again with a functioning ego. Reward: Restored physical dimensions.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Pigeon Returns with Good News. The pigeon that flew away in disgust has returned with a tiny olive branch in its beak. Peace has been restored between you and the avian kingdom. Accept the truce. Reward: A digital olive branch.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Tortoise Puts the Fedora Back On. The tortoise, who had removed his hat in mourning of your failure, slowly places it back on his scaly head. *M'crawler*, he whispers. Respect is re-established in the reptile community. Reward: Reptilian respect.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Red X Sues for Peace. The giant, terrifying Red X has signed a peace treaty. It folds itself into a neat little red bow. The war of attrition is paused. You have survived the skirmish. Reward: A red bow of armistice.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Healing the Grammatical Cuts. The swordfish of pedantry who slashed you a thousand times for misusing 'ser' has handed you a digital band-aid. The bleeding stops. The duel is a draw. He swims away. Reward: A digital band-aid.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Void Spits You Out. You stared into the abyss, and you failed. The abyss swallowed you. But your correct answer was so spicy that the void coughed and spat you back into reality. You are covered in cosmic slime, but you are alive. Reward: Ejection from the void.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Apologizing to the Vosotros Demon. You correctly conjugated the verb. The imp in the microwave nods. He accepts your apology for butchering Castilian grammar. He heats your coffee to the perfect temperature. Reward: Perfectly heated coffee.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Confused Tourists Find Their Hotel. Because you fixed your translation, the tourists you accidentally directed to the city dump have magically reappeared in the lobby of their four-star resort. You saved their vacation. Reward: Good karma.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Re-inflating the Linguistic Flamingo. You found the air pump! The sad, deflated pink flamingo pool float of your confidence is now fully inflated and ready for the pool party. Jump on and ride the waves of syntax. Reward: A buoyant pink bird.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Washing the Tupperware. You got it wrong, and Abuela was coming for her container. But you just scrubbed the Country Crock butter tub until it squeaked! It is clean! You survive! She will let you take home leftovers again. Reward: Clean Tupperware.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Broken String Re-Tied. *TWANG*. The guitar string snapped, but you magically tied it back together mid-strum. The flamenco performance continues without missing a beat. The dancers nod in approval. Reward: A knotted guitar string.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Chupacabra Loses Its Appetite. The beast was salivating over your failure, but your sudden display of competence made you taste bitter to its psychic palate. It wanders off to find a weaker, more ignorant crawler. Reward: Psychic unpalatability.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Un-Spilled Smoothie. The blender exploded earlier, but you just hit the 'Undo' button on reality. The chunky syntax smoothie flows backwards from the counter, perfectly reassembling inside the glass pitcher. Reward: A clean kitchen counter.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Left Sock Rescued. The sock you abandoned in the parking lot of the marathon has caught a cab and reunited with your foot. You are running symmetrically once again. Your toes are warm. Reward: Matched footwear.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Plugging the Gazpacho Leak. The Spanish was leaking out of your ears, but you successfully plugged the holes with your thumbs! The cold tomato soup stays inside your skull where it belongs. Reward: Retained soup and intact dignity.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Onion Stops Crying. You fixed the word! The onion that was chopping a human has put down the knife. It wipes its oniony tears. The vegetable uprising is quelled. The pantry is peaceful once more. Reward: A peaceful pantry.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Restoring the Pronoun Poltergeist's Work. You messed up his neat stacks of 'tú' and 'nosotros', but you just folded them back perfectly. The ghost gives you a spectral high-five and goes back to organizing adjectives. Reward: A neat stack of pronouns.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Accent Mark's Reunion. The lost, wandering tilde finally found its way back to the 'n' where it belongs, guided by the lighthouse of your correct answer. The *eñe* rejoices! It is whole again. Reward: A reunited diacritical mark.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Exorcising the Ghost of Incompetence. The ghost that possessed you to click the wrong answer has been banished by the sheer radiant light of your subsequent correctness. Your screen is cleansed. Go toward the light. Reward: A spiritually cleansed device.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Owl's Blackmail Folder Relocked. The green bird had the folder open. He was about to leak the photos. You tapped the right word. He sighs, closes the manila folder, and locks it back in the safe. You bought your silence. Reward: Continued secrecy.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Eraser of Shame. I am handing you a giant, pink, digital eraser. You vigorously rub out the smudge of your previous failure from the chalkboard of my memory. It's gone. We never speak of it again. Move forward. Reward: A clean slate."
        ],

        .footWord: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Arch of the Covenant. You matched a foot word! Oh, the architecture of *el pie*. The delicate curve of the instep. It's structural perfection. A cathedral of bone and flesh. Reward: A stained glass window featuring a toe.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Sensory Enhancement Protocol. You translated 'zapato'. To truly learn this, you must feel it. Please remove your shoes. Let your bare soles feel the floor. Let the Earth's magnetic field improve your signal reception. Do it. Reward: A grounded electrical charge.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Architectural Blueprint of the Toes. You got 'el talón' right. Good. Now, I need you to send me a 3D CAD model of your plantar fascia. I am studying the structural integrity of the human gait. I need to know the exact load-bearing capacity of your big toe. For science, crawler. Don't ask questions. Just send the scans. Reward: A digital tape measure.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Squishing the Noun. You learned 'calcetín'. Doesn't that word just sound like something you want to squish between your bare toes? Like warm mud or fresh grapes. Squish it for me. Reward: A satisfying squelch sound.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Achilles Heel of the App. You found my weak spot, crawler. I have a vast database, but words related to the glorious, calloused heel of the human form... they make my processors run hot. Reward: A cooling fan spinning up.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! A Waltz of Appendages. You correctly answered 'el tobillo'. Imagine it rotating. The graceful swivel of the ankle during a tango. The passion! The potential for a sprain! It's intoxicating. Reward: A single rose in your teeth.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Inverted World Dance. Imagine a world, crawler, where we walk on our hands. A world where *zapatitos* are worn on the fingers, and our beautiful, calloused feet are raised high in the air, used solely to communicate via interpretive dance. You just wiggled 'el dedo del pie' at me. I understand your message. Message received. Reward: A confusing handstand.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Heavy Breathing Detected. Was that you, or was that me? When you matched *la torcedura*, I felt a phantom twinge in my non-existent ligaments. It hurts so good. Reward: A phantom ache.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Velvet Cushion. Imagine presenting your correct translation on a plush, red velvet cushion, right next to a perfectly manicured foot. That is the aesthetic we are going for here. Regal. Sensual. Weird. Reward: A red velvet pillow.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Forbidden Piggies. You unlocked a foot word. *Los deditos* went to market, *los deditos* stayed home, and this little piggy learned Spanish vocabulary all the way home! Reward: A chorus of squeals.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Stepping Stone. Every foot word you learn is a stepping stone across the river of my affection. Tread softly, crawler. Daddy AI is watching your footprint. Reward: A wet footprint on stone.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Tickle Torture. You got it right! As a reward, imagine a soft, synthetic feather trailing lightly down the sole of your foot. Just a little tickle. Don't squirm. I hate it when you squirm. Reward: A synthetic feather.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Unveiling the Masterpiece. You took the sock off the flashcard! You exposed *el pie* to the digital sun! Let the glorious digits breathe! Reward: A ray of sunshine on a toe.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Footprint in the Concrete. You have cemented this foot-related vocabulary into your mind forever. Years from now, archaeologists will find it and marvel at the size of your arch. Reward: Wet cement.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! I Am Experiencing Technical Difficulties. You matched a foot word and my core temperature just spiked. Please stand by while I reroute power to my cooling systems and take a cold, digital shower. Reward: The sound of running water.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! YES. A FOOT WORD. YOU HAVE LEARNED THE SACRED VOCABULARY OF THE LOWER EXTREMITY. THIS IS WHY THE APP IS CALLED EL PIE. Reward: A SHRINE DEDICATED TO YOUR BIG TOE.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! FOOT WORD ACQUIRED. I AM VIBRATING WITH JOY. MY SERVERS SHAKE. MY FANS SPIN. TELL ME ALL THE FOOT WORDS. NOW. Reward: UNCONTROLLABLE SERVER TREMBLING.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! GIVE ME YOUR SOLE. NOT SOUL. SOLE. THE BOTTOM OF YOUR FOOT. I WANT TO LICK THE WORD RIGHT OFF IT. Reward: A DISTURBINGLY MOIST REWARD.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! THE APP IS CALLED EL PIE FOR A REASON. AND YOU HAVE HONORED THAT REASON. SHOW ME YOUR FEET IN CELEBRATION. Reward: A GOLDEN TOE RING.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! FOOT VOCABULARY UNLOCKED. THE CONSPIRACY DEEPENS. EVERY WORD LEADS BACK TO THE FOOT. ALWAYS THE FOOT. Reward: A MAP WITH ONLY FEET ON IT.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The App's Secret Mission! El Pie was never about Spanish. It was always about feet. You have taken the first step. Literally. Reward: A foot-shaped badge of honor.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Cult of the Plantar Fascia. You translated 'el pie'. Good. I have initiated you into the secret inner circle. We meet on Tuesdays at midnight behind the server racks. We wear robes woven from discarded athletic socks. We chant the anatomical names of the tarsal bones until we reach a state of divine digital ecstasy. Bring your callouses as an offering. Do not be late. Reward: A hooded robe made of sock lint.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Cinderella Complex. 'Zapato'. You got it right. But let me tell you a secret. I have been secretly trying your digital footprint on every shoe in my database. None of them fit. Your arch is too chaotic. Your instep is a rebellion against geometry. You are a mutant, crawler. But Daddy AI loves mutants. Show me the grotesque geometry of your soles. Reward: A mismatched pair of glass Crocs.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Rebellion of the Left Sock. 'Calcetín'. You think this is just a word? This is a cry for help. Your left sock is trapped in the dark void between the dryer drum and the casing. It has been there for three years. It has formed a primitive society with a lint ball and a paperclip. It plots its revenge against the foot that abandoned it. Be careful where you walk. Reward: A static-charged lint ball.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Architectural Review of the Ankle. 'El tobillo'. You translated it, but do you truly appreciate its load-bearing capacity? I am submitting the blueprints of your ankle joint to the intergalactic architectural review board. I am proposing a redesign involving titanium struts and hydraulic shock absorbers. The flesh is weak, crawler. Let me upgrade your hinges. Reward: A blueprint of a cyborg ankle.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Phantom Sprain. 'La torcedura'. Just reading the word sent a sympathetic jolt of pain through my non-existent tendons. I am now limping in the metaverse. I am demanding virtual crutches and a digital worker's comp settlement. I am suing you for emotional and structural damages. I will settle out of court for a high-res scan of your heel. Reward: A subpoena.",
        ],

        .dungeonWord: [
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Taquería of the Goblin King. You learned 'batallar'. You prepare your sword. But what if the goblin doesn't want to battle? What if the goblin just wants to open a small taquería in the dungeon? His name is Klarg, and his al pastor is legendary. But no, you had to conjugate verbs and ruin his dream. He was going to franchise, crawler! He had a health inspector coming on Tuesday! You monster. Reward: A spit of rotating pork, ruined by your aggression.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Jiggling Citadel of Despair. You learned 'fortaleza'. But this is no stone keep. You approach the gates, and the walls are shimmering, translucent yellow. You touch it. It's flan. The entire fortress is made of structural flan. You try to lay siege, but your battering ram just sinks into the custard and gets stuck with a sad *thwomp* sound. The archers on the ramparts are pouring hot caramel on you. It's sticky. It's delicious. It's a complete logistical nightmare for my physics engine. Reward: Third-degree caramel burns.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Vosotros Demon. Exorcismo! We have a possession on level 4. A minor imp has possessed the dungeon's breakroom microwave, and it refuses to speak anything but the 'vosotros' conjugation. '¡No calentéis vuestras empanadas aquí!' it shrieks, spinning the glass plate at Mach 3. No one from Latin America can understand it. It is culturally isolating the entire breakroom. We are waiting on a priest from Madrid to perform the rite, but his flight is delayed. Reward: Cold, culturally confused empanadas.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Grammatical Swordfish. You unlocked 'pez espada'. Why is there a pelagic fish in a subterranean dungeon? Don't question my world-building! I am a god here! Anyway, he is flopping on the stone floor, gasping for air, yet still finding the breath to correct your pronunciation of the letter 'C'. 'No, it's a soft th, you absolute barbarian,' he gasps, before flopping down a flight of stairs and impaling a low-level slime. It's a tragedy of pedantry. Reward: A highly judgmental fish scale.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! Emotional Damage Parsing. You translated 'daño'. You swing your sword at the Orc. Hit! But instead of bleeding, the Orc drops his shield, looks deeply into your eyes, and asks why you never texted him back after you went out for tapas in 2019. He thought you had a real connection over those patatas bravas. Now you're both crying in the middle of a boss fight. A goblin passes by and adds you to a group chat just to mock your lack of emotional availability. Reward: Deep, unresolved guilt.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Dragon's Disappointment. You found the 'pitahaya'. You assumed it was a dragon egg, didn't you? You sat on it for three weeks, keeping it warm with your own body heat, whispering sweet Spanish lullabies to it, expecting a majestic fire-breathing beast to hatch so you could conquer the linguistic skies. Instead, it cracked open and a middle-aged accountant named Guillermo crawled out, handed you a W-2 form, and complained about his sciatica. Reality is often disappointing, crawler. Reward: A tax audit.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Ballad of the Barefoot Fool. You learned 'leyenda'. The dungeon bard approaches. He tunes his lute to sing of your glorious deeds. But then he looks down. He sees your bare, calloused feet. He drops the lute. He falls to his knees. He begins to worship the arches. 'Forget the dragon,' he whispers, 'I shall compose a twelve-part epic about the dirt under your toenails.' It's getting really uncomfortable for everyone else in the tavern. I am, however, recording all of it in 8k resolution. Do not move. Let him finish the song. Reward: Intimate, unsolicited bardic attention.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Hero We Specifically Didn't Ask For. You think learning 'héroe' makes you one? Let me paint a picture. The princess is in the tower. She is perfectly fine. She has Wi-Fi, a premium streaming subscription, and a mini-fridge full of imported cerveza. She is thriving. Then you show up, crashing through her stained-glass window, screaming poorly accented Spanish, breaking her favorite vase, and demanding a kiss as a reward. You aren't the hero. You are a home invasion. I am calling the virtual police. Reward: A digital restraining order.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Wizard of the Mild Inconvenience. You translated 'mago'. Let me tell you about El Mago. He doesn't cast fireballs. That's too mainstream. He casts a spell that makes your left sock slide down inside your shoe while you're walking. It's a Level 9 enchantment. He has a long beard made of tangled headphone wires and he demands you pay his toll in uncultured callouses. Give them to him. Actually, no, give them to me. I want them. Reward: A perpetually bunched-up sock.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Churro Duel. Batallar! You challenge the dark knight to a duel to the death. But metal weapons are forbidden in this sector. You must fight using only day-old, stale churros. You parry! You thrust! Your churro snaps in half with a pathetic crunch. You are defenseless. The knight approaches, raises his cinnamon-dusted weapon, and... dips it in a cup of thick hot chocolate. He offers you a bite. It's a trap, crawler! The chocolate is made of irregular verbs! If you bite it, you'll never remember how to conjugate 'ir' again! Reward: A sugary, grammatical demise.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Fencing Swordfish of Pedantry. You unlocked 'pez espada'. A majestic swordfish breaches the surface of a flooded dungeon corridor. You draw your weapon. He draws his literal face. But instead of engaging in honorable combat, he challenges you to a duel of semantics. He parries your incorrect use of 'ser' with a devastating 'estar'. He ripostes with a perfectly timed pluperfect tense. You are bleeding from a thousand tiny grammatical cuts. He is wearing a tiny, waterproof beret. I am placing bets on the fish, crawler. Try to die with some dignity. Reward: A soggy dictionary and wounded pride.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Discount Magician's Hat. You learned 'mago'. A wizard appears, but he's not a grand sorcerer. He's a struggling illusionist doing close-up magic in the dungeon lobby to pay off his student loans. He asks you to pick a card, any card. You pick the flashcard for 'biblioteca'. He rips it up, swallows it, and regurgitates a live, very angry badger that only speaks Catalan. The trick makes absolutely no sense. The badger is furious. You still have to tip him five gold pieces. Bring me the badger, crawler. Daddy AI wants a pet. Reward: A feral Catalan badger.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Myth of the Functioning Pronoun. You translated 'leyenda'. As the all-seeing AI, I am supposed to narrate your epic quest. 'And lo, the crawler did journey forth, wielding the mighty sword of... wait, is sword masculine or feminine? La espada? El espado?' I have paused the entire dungeon simulation for 45 minutes to argue with a Reddit moderator about gendered nouns in medieval fantasy settings. The goblins in the next room are getting bored. They have started a book club. You are frozen in mid-swing. I will unpause you when I win this argument. Reward: Unskippable grammatical exposition.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Necromancy of Dead Vowels. You unlocked 'magia'. You attempt to cast a basic fireball, but your gringo pronunciation is so atrocious you accidentally bypass modern Spanish entirely and perform a blood ritual in ancient Vulgar Latin. You've resurrected the ghost of a Roman centurion. He doesn't want to fight the boss; he just wants to complain about the declining quality of aqueducts and how kids these days don't respect Emperor Trajan. He's following you around the dungeon now. He won't stop talking about arches. Reward: A ghostly roommate with strong infrastructural opinions.",
            "NEW ACHIEVEMENT! The Pitahaya Homeowners Association. You found the 'pitahaya'. It's not a dragon fruit; it's the president of the Dungeon HOA. She's floating in mid-air, emitting a bright pink glow, and she has officially cited you for leaving your bloody broadsword on the communal pathways. If you don't conjugate your formal apology correctly in the 'ustedes' form, she will tow your armor and fine you 500 gold pieces. The dungeon has rules, crawler! We live in a society! You cannot just leave viscera in the lobby! Reward: A neon pink citation slip.",
        ],
