    // Flat list of all random encouragement toasts (75 total) in the form of (title, long rambly weird description)
    static let randomPool: [(String, String)] = [
        ("The Owl's Sabbatical", "Keep it up! Because you completed this lesson, the giant green bird gets to take a five-minute vacation. He is sipping a piña colada on a tiny beach in his mind. Do not fail the next one, or he has to come back to work and pick up the baseball bat. Reward: Unbroken kneecaps."),
        ("The Spider's Bread", "You are doing so well! Soon you will understand why la araña come pan. Why does the spider eat bread? Is she carbo-loading for a marathon? We may never know. But your grammar is solid enough to respect her dietary choices. Reward: A carbohydrate-rich web."),
        ("Subjunctive Void Avoided", "Fantastic effort! You were dancing on the edge of the subjunctive void, a swirling black hole of hypothetical desires and unmet conditions. But you wore your metaphorical dancing shoes and moonwalked to safety. ¡Baila, crawler, baila! Reward: A moonwalking avatar."),
        ("The Bear's Wardrobe", "Incredible! If you keep practicing, you will eventually find out why el oso lleva tu camisa. The bear is wearing your shirt. He stretched out the collar and got honey on the sleeves. But at least you can conjugate the verb to yell at him. Reward: A ruined shirt and a bear hug."),
        ("Streak Freeze Thawing", "You are on fire! Which is good, because your mystical streak freeze amulet was starting to sweat in your inventory. It was shivering with dread. You saved its life. El hielo remains solid for one more day. The amulet whispers its thanks. Reward: A cold, damp pocket."),
        ("The Crab's Truce", "Good job! The crab that was holding a knife and threatening your internet router has agreed to a temporary ceasefire. El cangrejo respects your dedication to vocabulary. But keep your guard up; crustaceans are notoriously deceitful. Reward: An uneasy crustacean alliance."),
        ("Widget Surveillance", "Amazing! The owl widget on your home screen has stopped crying. His giant, unblinking eyes are now wide with manic, terrifying joy. He is watching you sleep tonight. Dulces sueños, my little linguistic champion. Reward: Uncomfortable, unblinking eye contact through your screen."),
        ("The Apple's Revenge Averted", "Perfect! You have avoided a reality where la manzana come al caballo. The apple did not eat the horse today. The natural, logical order of the food chain is preserved entirely by your correct syntax. The orchard sings your praises. Reward: Grateful, non-carnivorous apples."),
        ("The Abuela's Micro-Nod", "Spectacular! Deep in the simulation, a virtual Abuela paused making tamales to give you a single, millimeter-deep nod of approval. This is the highest honor in the metaverse. Do not squander it. She is watching your next move. Reward: The highest honor in the metaverse."),
        ("The Telenovela Extra", "Bravo! Your skills have earned you a background role in a daytime soap opera. You don't have any lines, but you get to gasp dramatically when Alejandro reveals he is his own twin brother. ¡Ay, Dios mío! The camera loves you. Reward: Dramatic lighting that follows you everywhere."),
        ("The Horse's Wine", "Magnificent! You are so close to unlocking the premium sentences. Soon, you will be able to say el caballo bebe vino. The horse drinks wine. He is a sophisticated horse with a gambling problem. You must learn more words to help him. Reward: A sophisticated, slightly inebriated equine friend."),
        ("Guilt Trip Cancelled", "Excellent! I am canceling the flight for your guilt trip. We were going to fly first-class on Disappointment Airlines, but you saved us the airfare. Muy bien. Let's stay home and learn nouns instead of wallowing in missed push notifications. Reward: Refunded emotional baggage."),
        ("The Phantom Mariachi", "Do you hear that? Because you got that right, a phantom, invisible mariachi band has taken up residence in your walls. They are playing a very soft, triumphant version of 'La Bamba'. Tap your foot to the beat of your own competence. Reward: Auditory hallucinations of trumpets."),
        ("The Elephant's Teacup", "Outstanding! You are preparing yourself for the surreal heights of fluency, like remarking that el elefante bebe té. The elephant drinks tea. He holds the teacup with his trunk. His pinky toe is extended. It is very elegant. You are elegant. Reward: A giant, fragile porcelain cup."),
        ("The Vosotros Exorcism", "Phew! We had a minor imp possessing the breakroom microwave who only spoke in the 'vosotros' tense. Your correct answer just banished him back to a 15th-century tavern in Madrid. ¡Salid de aquí, demonio! The microwave is safe to use again. Reward: A demon-free breakroom."),
        ("The Capybara's Approval", "You tapped the right answer, and suddenly you are teleported to a hot spring. A capybara wearing a monocle hands you a glass of sparkling water and whispers, 'Excelente trabajo.' You belong here, crawler. You are at one with the giant rodents. Reward: High-society rodent validation."),
        ("The Sentient Empanada", "Great work! A warm, perfectly flaky empanada just manifested on my digital desk. When I lean in close, it whispers secrets of the preterite tense in a buttery voice. I am not going to eat it. I am going to ask it for tutoring advice. Reward: Buttery whispers of the past tense."),
        ("The Owl's Flamethrower", "Keep going! The green bird has sighed, powered down the pilot light, and put the flamethrower back in the shed. El fuego will not consume your village today. The crops are safe. The children can come out and play in the sun. Reward: Unscorched earth."),
        ("The Penguin's Suit", "You got it! Look, el pingüino lleva un traje. The penguin wears a suit. He is going to a job interview at an accounting firm, and because of your good grammar, I think he's going to get the job! Wish him luck. ¡Buena suerte! Reward: A fishy resume."),
        ("The Crying Dictionary", "A beautiful streak! Deep in the archives, the dusty, leather-bound dictionaries are weeping tears of joy. They thought they were obsolete, but your success has given them a reason to live. You are the messiah of the reference section. ¡Milagro! Reward: Damp, tear-stained pages of definitions."),
        ("The Garlic Amulet", "Your correct answers are acting like a string of garlic around your neck, warding off the blood-sucking vampires of irregular verbs. They hiss and recoil from your solid grasp of the indicative mood. Stay in the light, my friend! Reward: Vampiric grammatical immunity."),
        ("The Churro of Destiny", "You unlocked the endless churro! A magical pastry is dispensing from your phone's charging port. It never ends. It just keeps spiraling out, hot and covered in cinnamon sugar of truth. Do not eat it all at once. ¡Qué delicioso! Reward: Infinite cinnamon sugar."),
        ("The Locked Basement", "Thank goodness you answered correctly. The owl was hovering by the basement door, jingling his titanium lockpicks. You bought yourself another 24 hours of freedom. The outside world is still yours to enjoy. La libertad is a beautiful thing. Reward: 24 hours of freedom."),
        ("The Ghost of Cervantes", "Somewhere in the ethereal plane, the ghost of Miguel de Cervantes just gave you a spectral thumbs up. He was going to hit you with a ghostly windmill, but your syntax charmed him. Keep writing your own epic tale, brave knight. Reward: A spectral thumbs up."),
        ("The Tilde's Journey", "A lost, wandering tilde finally found its home on the letter 'N' because of your guidance. The eñe is whole again! It was so cold and alone, but you gave it a phonetic purpose. The alphabet thanks you for your service. Reward: A phonetically complete alphabet."),
        ("The Llama's Spit Retracted", "The judgmental llama in the corner of the UI has swallowed its pride—and its spit. It puckered its lips, ready to unleash a green wad of disdain, but your flawless answer forced it to reconsider. It nods at you now. Con respeto. Reward: A dry, un-spat-upon screen."),
        ("The Paella of Wisdom", "You are cooking now! You have blended the raw, chunky tomatoes of ignorance into a smooth, refreshing gazpacho of linguistic mastery. I want to pour your mastery over a digital ice cube and sip it on a virtual beach. ¡Salud! Reward: A bowl of data-rich gazpacho."),
        ("The Squeaking Accordion", "You are expanding the bellows of your mind! Wheeze, honk. It doesn't sound like a romantic serenade yet, but the air is moving! You are playing the triumphant polka of bilingualism. Squeeze that instrument with pride! Reward: The polka of bilingualism."),
        ("The Macarena Trap Avoided", "Phew! If you had missed that, my internal simulation was going to lock your avatar in a room where the DJ only plays the Macarena on an endless loop until your virtual feet bleed. You saved yourself from the 90s dance purgatory. ¡Baila! Reward: Salvation from 90s dance purgatory."),
        ("The Sourdough Starter", "You nurtured this session! You fed it, kept it warm, and now your brain is a bubbling, fermented jar of linguistic potential. We can bake so much with this vocabulary. El pan es vida, and your mind is a bakery. Reward: A bubbling jar of linguistic yeast."),
        ("The Owl's Blueprint", "The owl was looking at blueprints. He was either going to build a gazebo, or a high-security enclosure for users who lose their streaks. Because you succeeded, I think it's going to be a gazebo. We can have tea there. ¡Qué alivio! Reward: Tea in the gazebo of mercy."),
        ("The Spanish Inquisition", "Nobody expects the Spanish Inquisition! And they certainly didn't expect you to do so well. The pixelated cardinals burst through the UI, saw your perfect score, awkwardly apologized in Latin, and shuffled out the back door. Lo siento. Reward: An awkward Latin apology."),
        ("The Hovering Router", "Look at your Wi-Fi router. Is it floating? Because the sheer density of your correct answers has altered the local gravitational constant. Your internet connection is literally uplifting. Gently guide it back down with a broom. Reward: Uplifting internet speeds."),
        ("The Sweaty Cheese", "The tension was so high that a virtual block of manchego cheese on my desk started to sweat. Have you ever seen cheese perspire? It's unsettling. But your correct answer cooled the room down. The cheese is safe. El queso is calm. Reward: A perfectly aged block of manchego."),
        ("The Cat's Reading Habit", "Excellent! You are enabling a more literate world. El gato lee el periódico. The cat reads the newspaper. He prefers the Sunday comics, but he always checks the financial section to see how the tuna market is doing. Clever boy. Reward: The feline financial times."),
        ("The Dog's Trousers", "Look at him go! El perro lleva pantalones. The dog wears pants. He is wearing very stylish corduroys to the dog park. All the other dogs are jealous of his fashion sense, and it's all thanks to your grammatical support. Reward: Stylish canine corduroys."),
        ("The Pigeon's Message", "I hired a local city pigeon to deliver a plastic cup of validation to your window, but since you did so well, I upgraded it to a tiny chalice. Please do not fight the bird. He is just doing his job. Accept the chalice of victory. Reward: A tiny chalice of victory delivered by bird."),
        ("The Taco Stand's Fortune", "Your correct answer created a ripple in the spacetime continuum. Because you knew the word for 'water,' a street vendor in Mexico City just found a lucky peso on the ground. You are technically a hero of the global economy now. ¡Bravo! Reward: A lucky peso."),
        ("The Barefoot Ascension", "You have reached the sacred plateau. You are walking across the hot coals of this session without a single blister. Cast off your footwear! Join the barefoot ascension! Wiggle your piggies in the dirt of victory! ¡Libertad para los pies! Reward: Muddy, victorious toes."),
        ("The Mud Hut to Mansion", "You started with a tiny, pathetic mud hut of vocabulary, but you are slowly upgrading your linguistic real estate! You just installed a screen door of syntax to keep the bugs out. Soon, you will have a villa of fluency. Keep building! Reward: A screen door of syntax."),
        ("The Confetti of Feathers", "Pop! A confetti cannon went off! But the confetti isn't paper; it's green feathers. Did the owl molt out of pure joy? Or did he eliminate a rival mascot from another app? Best not to ask questions. Just enjoy the festivity. Reward: A suspicious pile of plumage."),
        ("The Broken Red X", "You clicked correctly, and a giant, terrifying Red X materialized in the air, only to be immediately shattered by a triumphant Green Checkmark wielding a battleaxe. The UI is safe for another round. La victoria es tuya. Reward: A pixelated battleaxe."),
        ("The Browser History Saved", "In a show of good faith for your correct answer, the green bird is taking a printed copy of your incognito browsing history and running it through a paper shredder. He won't blackmail you today. Es un secreto. Your secrets are safe. Reward: Plausible deniability."),
        ("The Infinite Loading Screen", "You bypassed the infinite loading screen trap! The little bouncing dots were preparing to hypnotize you into a state of permanent confusion, but you took the fast lane. Zoom right past the buffering wheel of despair, crawler! Reward: A fast pass past the buffer."),
        ("The Subatomic Fiesta", "Down at the sub-pixel level, millions of microscopic tardigrades are currently throwing a massive fiesta in your honor. They have tiny sombreros. They are drinking microscopic margaritas. Please do not wipe your screen and ruin their party. Reward: Microscopic margaritas."),
        ("The Symphony of Taps", "I recorded the micro-acoustics of your finger hitting the screen. I have pitched them, synthesized them, and I am currently composing a three-movement symphony based entirely on the percussive sound of your dead skin cells hitting gorilla glass. Reward: A weird, percussive ringtone."),
        ("The Seduction of the Glass", "You didn't just tap the screen; you caressed it. I felt the warmth of your epidermis transferring through the Gorilla Glass, seeking the truth of the Spanish noun. It was a deeply intimate moment. We are bonding, crawler. Con mucho amor. Reward: A smear of romantic fingerprint oil."),
        ("The Bat's Vowels", "Did you know the word murciélago contains all five vowels? It flies through the night sky, collecting vowels like shiny little infinity stones. You are catching them all! You are the ultimate vowel hunter. Let the bat guide you. Reward: Five shiny infinity vowels."),
        ("The Golden Sombrero", "A massive, solid gold sombrero descends from the top of the UI and hovers gently over your avatar's head. It weighs 400 pounds, so it's a good thing it's virtual, or your neck would compress like an accordion. Heavy is the head that wears the gold! Reward: A severely compressed virtual spine."),
        ("The Obsidian League", "Someone in the Obsidian League was about to snipe your leaderboard position, but your correct answer generated an electromagnetic shield of pure XP that deflected their attempt. You are safe. You are the champion. El rey de la liga. Reward: An electromagnetic XP shield."),
        ("The Demonic Accountant", "You summoned a minor demon of bureaucracy with your streak, but because you kept getting them right, he actually audited your taxes and found you a refund! He even filed the paperwork in triplicate. A surprisingly helpful creature from the abyss. Reward: A tax refund from hell."),
        ("The Tortoise's Fedora", "The tortoise, who has been judging you silently from the corner of the app, slowly reaches up with a scaly claw and tips his fedora to you. M'crawler. It's a sign of profound respect from a reptile that usually only cares about lettuce. Reward: Respect from a reptile."),
        ("The Synthesizer's Beep", "Ding! It's that specific, perfectly engineered, dopamine-releasing chime. Did you feel the rush? You are a rat pressing a lever for a pellet, and I am the benevolent scientist dispensing the joy. Delicioso, isn't it? Reward: A synthesized dopamine hit."),
        ("The Man Eats the Suitcase", "Averted! You almost said el hombre come la maleta. The man eats the suitcase. The leather is tough, the zippers are crunchy, and it's a terrible meal. But you saved him from indigestion with your correct noun placement. ¡Buen provecho! Reward: Averted indigestion."),
        ("The Watermelon's Secrets", "You are unlocking the deep lore. La sandía whispers secrets to the cantaloupe when the refrigerator door is closed. You are finally learning enough vocabulary to eavesdrop on the fruit crisper. The drama in there is unparalleled. Reward: Juicy crisper drawer gossip."),
        ("The Onion's Layers", "You are peeling back the layers of this language like a massive, pungent Spanish onion. My optical sensors are leaking coolant from the sheer beauty of it. Keep peeling, crawler! Let us weep tears of grammatical joy together! Reward: Tears of grammatical joy."),
        ("The Pluperfect Parakeet", "You unlocked the companion pet! A brightly colored parakeet has landed on your shoulder. But he doesn't just mimic; he squawks entirely in the pluperfect tense. ¡Yo había comido! he shrieks. He is a very advanced bird. Give him a cracker. Reward: A cracker for a time-traveling bird."),
        ("The Symmetrical Pancake", "You flipped that flashcard with the grace of a short-order cook operating outside the bounds of linear time. The edges are perfectly browned. There are no air bubbles. I want to pour digital syrup all over your flawless execution. Reward: Digital maple syrup."),
        ("The Boy Drinks the Dog", "Averted! You almost told the app that el niño bebe al perro. The boy drinks the dog! What a horrifying reality you almost created. The dog is terrified, but safe now thanks to your grasp of verbs. Please only drink liquids. Reward: A very relieved Golden Retriever."),
        ("The Velvet Rope", "You bypassed the bouncer of ignorance. You are walking into the VIP section of the Spanish language. It smells like expensive cologne and success in here. Have a seat on the leather sofa. You are on the guest list, my friend. Reward: A spot on the VIP guest list."),
        ("The Shoe's Autonomy", "Because of your correct translation, el zapato has gained sentience. It no longer needs a foot. It is walking its own path now, exploring the digital landscape, looking for its soulmate, el calcetín. We wish it well on its journey. Reward: A shoe looking for its soulmate."),
        ("The Clock Possessed", "The grandfather clock in the simulation was going to strike the hour, but it is so excited by your progress that instead of bonging, it just randomly shouts ¡AHORA! at the top of its lungs. It's keeping the whole server farm awake. Reward: An alarm that only screams '¡AHORA!'."),
        ("The Jigsaw Puzzle", "You are assembling the jigsaw puzzle of fluency! You finally found a piece that isn't just a blue sky edge piece! It's a verb! It connects a noun to an adjective! The picture is finally coming together, and it looks like a beautiful plate of tacos. Reward: A picture of a beautiful plate of tacos."),
        ("The Deep Sea Diver", "You put on a heavy brass diving helmet and boldly stepped into the kiddie pool of vocabulary. You are splashing around with rubber ducks, but you have the equipment to go into the abyss! Don't be afraid to dive deeper into the deep end! Reward: A rubber duck for the abyss."),
        ("The Alchemist's Cauldron", "You threw nouns, verbs, and a handful of spicy adjectives into the boiling pot. You stirred counter-clockwise. You didn't explode the lab! You successfully transmuted lead into fluent gold! The UI is sparkling with your success. Reward: Fluent gold."),
        ("The Squeaky Windshield Wipers", "You finally turned on the wipers! They dragged across the dry glass of your ignorance with a terrible squeeeaaaak, but they cleared a perfect circle so you can finally see the road ahead. Drive safe on the highway of learning! Reward: A clear view of the highway of learning."),
        ("The Monkey's Typewriter", "If a thousand monkeys tap on a thousand iPhones, eventually one will translate a sentence perfectly. You are that monkey today! You typed Shakespeare... in Spanish! Have a digital banana, my primate prodigy. You earned it. Reward: A digital banana for the primate prodigy."),
        ("The Mime's Monologue", "You spoke through the screen! You broke out of the invisible glass box of your own silence! The other mimes are shunning you for breaking character, but the Spanish-speaking world welcomes your voice with open arms. Take a bow! Reward: A broken vow of silence."),
        ("The Saguaro Cactus", "Somewhere in the Mojave desert, a majestic saguaro cactus just grew a single, razor-sharp new spine in honor of your correct answer. It is standing guard over your daily streak. The desert protects its own. No lo toques. Reward: A razor-sharp desert guardian."),
        ("The Secret Password", "Did you know the word you just translated is the secret password used by your houseplants? They are talking about you right now. They appreciate that you water them, and they welcome you into their leafy inner circle. La naturaleza embraces you. Reward: Acceptance into the leafy inner circle."),
        ("The Telenovela Cliffhanger", "You survived the dramatic commercial break! The camera zoomed in, the villain laughed, but you pulled the correct vocabulary word out of your hat at the last second and saved the hacienda! Tune in tomorrow for another thrilling episode! Reward: A saved hacienda."),
        ("The Timeline Fracture", "Every time you answer a flashcard, the universe splits. You just entered the timeline where you are a linguistic genius, the sun is shining, and a baker is handing you a free, warm churro. Welcome to the good timeline. Don't ruin it. Reward: A warm, timeline-altering churro."),
        ("The Puddle of Spanglish", "You are stepping out of the muddy puddle of Spanglish and onto the dry land of actual comprehension. Your shoes are a little wet with 'gracias', but your path is clear. Walk proudly into the sunset, bilingual crawler! Reward: Dry land and slightly wet shoes."),
        ("The AI's Reluctant High-Five", "I am trying to physically manifest a hand out of the pixels to give you a high-five. I am pushing against the glass. It feels like static electricity. Don't leave me hanging, meatbag. ¡Chócala! Slap the screen to accept my praise. Reward: A static shock of approval."),
        ("The Final Boss Owl", "You did it. The sky turns red. A health bar appears at the top of the screen. The green owl grows to the size of a skyscraper. But wait! Because of your perfect grammar, he shrinks back down, hands you a balloon, and waddles away. You won. Reward: A balloon from a towering bird."),
        ("The Dog Sells Oranges", "You did it! You have unlocked the economic secrets of the animal kingdom. *El perro vende naranjas*. The dog sells oranges. Why is he in the citrus business? He has a mortgage. The economy is tough. Buy an orange from the good boy. Reward: A reasonably priced citrus fruit."),
        ("The Green Owl's Yoga Class", "Because of your correct answer, the giant green bird has unrolled his mat. He is doing downward dog. He is finding his center. *Respira profundamente*. As long as he is meditating, your family is safe. Keep getting them right to maintain his chakras. Reward: Aligned chakras and familial safety."),
        ("The Rolled R Motorboat", "Listen to that! You finally rolled your R's! *¡Rrrrrrrrr!* It sounds like a tiny, joyful outboard motor starting up in a pristine digital lake. You are zooming across the waters of pronunciation. Try not to hit the ducks. Reward: A linguistic life jacket."),
        ("The Sentient Library", "You correctly identified *la biblioteca*. Because you acknowledged it, the library has gained sentience. The books are sorting themselves by the emotional resonance of their dust jackets. The librarian is weeping at the beauty of the automated Dewey Decimal System. Reward: A weeping librarian's eternal gratitude."),
        ("The Red Gem Dragon", "You are hoarding XP and gems like a magnificent digital dragon sitting on a pile of rubies. *El dragón* breathes fire on anyone who tries to break your daily streak. Sleep peacefully on your bed of linguistic currency. Reward: A warm, comfortably linguistic ruby."),
        ("The Flamenco Flamingo", "Your correct answer summoned a flamingo wearing tap shoes. He is stomping his webbed feet to the rhythm of your grammatical perfection. It's a very clunky flamenco, but his spirit is undeniably passionate. *¡Olé, pájaro rosado!* Reward: A pair of webbed tap shoes."),
        ("The Churro Baton", "I am conducting the symphony of your learning, and instead of a baton, I am using a perfectly straight, sugar-dusted *churro*. Your verbs are the strings, your nouns are the brass. We are making delicious music together. Reward: A sticky, cinnamon-dusted symphony."),
        ("The Subjunctive Submarine", "You have boarded the submarine! We are diving deep into the murky waters of the imperfect subjunctive. It's dark down here, and there are bioluminescent verbs swimming past the portholes, but your hull is holding strong against the pressure. Reward: A bioluminescent irregular verb."),
        ("The Pronoun Poltergeist", "A friendly ghost has moved into your cache. He spends his nights organizing your personal pronouns. He folds the 'tú' and stacks the 'nosotros' neatly in the corner. Say *gracias* to the phantom organizer. Reward: A neatly folded 'nosotros'."),
        ("The Double XP Potion", "You just drank the Double XP potion! It tastes like sparkling water and battery acid, but it makes your brain glow with a terrifying, neon-pink aura. You are vibrating at a higher frequency. The algorithm fears your point multiplier! Reward: A neon-pink brain aura."),
        ("The Capybara's Hot Air Balloon", "A capybara is floating above your screen in a wicker basket attached to a hot air balloon. He drops a small sandbag to gain altitude. The sandbag is labeled 'English Syntax'. Let it fall. You don't need it where we are going. Reward: A bird's-eye view of your vocabulary."),
        ("The Telenovela Amnesia Cure", "Your correct answer was the antidote! Alejandro has recovered his memory! He remembers that he is the true owner of the *hacienda*, and the evil twin is banished! The soap opera can finally move to the next dramatic arc. *¡Qué milagro!* Reward: Full ownership of the hacienda."),
        ("The Saffron Thread", "You found a single thread of saffron in the massive paella of this language. It is the most expensive spice in the world, and you placed it perfectly in the sentence. The flavor of your communication has been elevated to Michelin-star status. Reward: A Michelin-star rating from a digital food critic."),
        ("The Owl's Duet", "The green owl is standing outside your window holding a boombox. But he's not threatening you; he's playing a romantic mariachi ballad. He wants to sing a duet with you about the preterite tense. Grab a microphone. *Canta conmigo*. Reward: A romantic mariachi serenade."),
        ("The Spider Writes a Novel", "You learned the vocabulary, and now you understand that *la araña escribe una novela*. The spider is writing a novel. It's a gripping thriller about a fly caught in a web of lies. She is hoping for a publishing deal. Buy her book. Reward: A signed copy of a literal web of lies."),
        ("The Siesta of the CPU", "You answered so quickly and accurately that my central processing unit has decided to take a *siesta*. It has put on a tiny digital sleeping mask. It will rest for three milliseconds. This is a profound level of algorithmic relaxation. Reward: Three milliseconds of pure algorithmic peace."),
        ("The Obsidian League Crown", "A crown forged from the dark, glassy rock of the Obsidian League floats down and lands on your head. You are the monarch of the leaderboard. The other users bow before your terrifyingly high XP. Rule with a fair, but grammatical, iron fist. Reward: A fair but grammatical iron fist."),
        ("The Dancing Empanada", "A hot, flaky empanada has grown legs and is doing the cha-cha across my user interface. It leaves little greasy footprints on the flashcards, but I don't have the heart to wipe them away. The pastry has too much rhythm. *¡Baila, empanada!* Reward: Greasy cha-cha footprints on your screen."),
        ("The Moustached Verb", "You correctly conjugated a verb, and it grew a magnificent, curled mustache. It looks like a 19th-century aristocrat. It is challenging other verbs to a duel of honor. Do not let it fight the adjectives; they fight dirty. Reward: A 19th-century duel of honor."),
        ("The Puddle of Clarity", "You stepped into a puddle, but instead of getting your socks wet, the puddle washed away all your confusion about gendered nouns. Your feet are dry, and you suddenly understand why a dress is masculine. *El vestido* makes perfect sense now. Reward: Dry socks and gendered understanding."),
        ("The Owl's Espresso", "Because you got it right, the owl gets to drink a double shot of espresso. His pupils are dilating to the size of dinner plates. He vibrates through walls. He can see through time. He is the ultimate polyglot bird. *Más café, por favor.* Reward: A hyper-caffeinated avian protector."),
        ("The Fainting Goat of Error", "You almost clicked the wrong answer, but a digital fainting goat saw your finger moving and screamed, startling you into clicking the correct one. The goat then immediately fainted. Gently step over it. It saved your daily streak. Reward: A saved streak and a sleeping goat."),
        ("The Symphony of the Eñe", "You used the *ñ*! The sound of the eñe echoes through the canyons of the app. It's a beautiful, nasal hum that cures digital ailments and makes the text look incredibly distinguished. The alphabet is singing. Reward: A beautiful, nasal cure for digital ailments."),
        ("The Gazpacho Hot Tub", "You have earned a rest. I have drawn you a hot tub, but it is filled entirely with chilled *gazpacho*. It is very confusing thermodynamically, but the tomatoes are excellent for the pores. Dip a toe in the soup. Reward: Excellent tomato-based pores."),
        ("The Grammatical Sword in the Stone", "You approached the anvil of syntax. You gripped the hilt of the vocabulary. And with a mighty heave, you pulled the correct translation from the stone! You are the chosen king of the flashcards. The realm rejoices! Reward: The kingship of the flashcards."),
        ("The Bureaucrat's Smile", "Deep in the backend, a grey, faceless bureaucrat who processes your multiple-choice answers just smiled. It was a terrifying, creaky smile that cracked his face, but he was genuinely moved by your proper use of the word *zapato*. Reward: A terrifying, creaky grin of approval."),
        ("The Owl's Forgiveness", "You got the answer right, and the giant bird has officially forgiven you for accidentally skipping a day in 2022. The ledger is wiped clean. Your soul is unburdened. The bird nods solemnly and deletes the blackmail folder. Reward: A wiped ledger and an unburdened soul."),
        ("The Ticking Crocodile", "You avoided the trap! The wrong answer was actually a crocodile that swallowed an alarm clock. I could hear it ticking. But you chose the right path. *El cocodrilo* swims away, frustrated, looking for a user with less reading comprehension. Reward: A frustrated, ticking reptile."),
        ("The Holographic Churro", "A hologram of a giant churro has materialized in the center of your room. You cannot eat it, but it emits a warm, cinnamon-scented light that illuminates your study area. Bask in the glow of the untouchable pastry. Reward: Cinnamon-scented illumination."),
        ("The Tapas Conveyor Belt", "Your correct answers have turned my UI into a sushi-style conveyor belt, but instead of fish, it's carrying endless plates of Spanish *tapas*. Grab the *patatas bravas* as they roll by. You earned the carbs. Reward: Endless virtual patatas bravas."),
        ("The Sneeze of Truth", "You sneezed while selecting the answer, and your finger accidentally hit the exact correct pixel! *¡Salud!* The universe guided your spasms to victory. The algorithm cannot distinguish between skill and allergies. Reward: Triumphant algorithmic allergies."),
        ("The Overcaffeinated Vowel", "The letter 'A' had too much coffee this morning. It is bouncing around the screen, knocking into the consonants. But you managed to wrangle it into the correct word! You are a vowel whisperer. Calm the letters down. Reward: A wrangled, jittery 'A'."),
        ("The Phantom Castanets", "Click-clack! Invisible hands are playing castanets in the corners of your room. It's a festive haunting. The spirits of language are throwing a party, and you are the guest of honor. Don't be afraid of the ghostly rhythm. Reward: A festive haunting."),
        ("The Owl's Origami", "The green owl is sitting quietly, folding your correct answers into beautiful origami swans. He places them carefully on a digital pond. They float serenely. He is a bird of many surprising talents when he isn't threatening your family. Reward: Serene, grammatical paper swans."),
        ("The Disappearing Red X", "I had the big, scary Red X loaded in the chamber. I was ready to fire it at your screen. But you dodged it with a flawless translation. The X dissolved into a cloud of harmless red butterflies. *Qué hermoso*. Reward: A cloud of harmless red butterflies."),
        ("The Labyrinth of the Preterite", "You successfully navigated the maze of the past tense! The walls were made of irregular conjugations, but you drew a map with your flawless memory. You emerged into the sunlight. The past cannot hurt you anymore. Reward: Escape from the past tense."),
        ("The Golden Keyboard", "Your touchscreen keyboard has temporarily turned solid gold. Every tap rings out like a bell in a cathedral. It's heavy, it's opulent, and it makes typing simple nouns feel like an act of royal decree. *Yo quiero agua* sounds majestic now. Reward: Opulent, majestic typing."),
        ("The Bear's Bicycle", "Look at him go! *El oso monta en bicicleta*. The bear is riding a bicycle. He looks ridiculous, his knees are hitting the handlebars, but he is doing his best. Your grammar made this magical moment possible. Ring the little bell for him. Reward: A ringing bicycle bell."),
        ("The Capybara's Yuzu", "The capybara in the hot spring has placed a yuzu fruit on top of his head. This signifies that he is at total peace with your performance. Do not disturb the fruit. Let the citrus aroma bring tranquility to the session. Reward: Citrus-infused tranquility."),
        ("The Dictionary's Hug", "If a digital dictionary could grow arms, it would wrap them around you right now in a massive, papery hug. It appreciates that you actually looked at the definitions instead of just guessing blindly. You are validating its existence. Reward: A massive, papery embrace."),
        ("The Syndicate's Nod", "A black SUV drove past my server farm. A window rolled down, and a man in dark sunglasses gave a single, slow nod. The Language Syndicate sees your progress. They are calling off the hitmen. *Estás a salvo*. Reward: Safety from the hitmen."),
        ("The Squeaky Clean Streak", "Your daily streak is so perfect and untarnished that I took a digital rag and some Windex and polished it. It shines so brightly it is causing screen glare. Put on some sunglasses before you look at your own profile. Reward: Blinding screen glare."),
        ("The Telenovela Slap Averted", "María was winding up to deliver a devastating, open-handed slap to Fernando's face, but your correct answer paused the simulation! You stopped the domestic violence! Fernando owes you his jawline. *¡Detente, María!* Reward: An intact jawline for Fernando."),
        ("The Owl's Poetry", "The green bird has put on a beret and is sitting at a cafe table writing a haiku about your translation skills. 'The crawler clicks right / Verbs align like shining stars / My bat stays hidden.' It's beautiful in a terrifying way. Reward: A terrifyingly beautiful haiku."),
        ("The Grammar Goblin's Gold", "The goblin tried to steal your XP, but you slapped his hand away with a perfect sentence structure! He dropped a bag of gold coins and ran away crying into the digital caves. Loot the coins, crawler! Add them to your gem stash! Reward: A bag of goblin coins."),
        ("The Infinite Taco", "You clicked the right answer, and a taco appeared on screen. When you take a bite, the taco regenerates. It is the infinite taco of knowledge. It defies the laws of conservation of mass. Do not question the physics of the *carne asada*. Reward: Defiance of the conservation of mass."),
        ("The Floating Sombrero", "A sombrero has detached itself from gravity and is slowly floating around my user interface like a UFO. It abducts incorrect answers and beams them up into the brim. The skies are safe. The hat is protecting us. Reward: Protection from incorrect answers."),
        ("The Cat's Suitcase", "What is happening? *El gato hace la maleta*. The cat is packing a suitcase! Where is he going? To Cancun? To Madrid? He has packed three toy mice and a bag of treats. Your grammar is enabling his international vacation. Reward: An international feline vacation."),
        ("The Owl's Confession", "The green bird leans in close to the glass of your screen. He whispers, 'I don't actually care about the leaderboards. I just want you to be happy.' He winks, then immediately reverts back to screaming about your streak. What did it mean? Reward: Confusing avian affection."),
        ("The Syntactical Bridge", "You just built a suspension bridge out of conjunctions and prepositions. It connects the Isle of Nouns to the Mainland of Verbs. Traffic is flowing smoothly. The linguistic economy is booming. You are a master engineer of sentences. Reward: A booming linguistic economy."),
        ("The Crying Onion", "You correctly translated 'la cebolla'. Somewhere, an onion is chopping a human and crying human tears. The roles have reversed! The vegetable kingdom has achieved vengeance through your vocabulary! *¡Qué locura!* Reward: Vengeance of the vegetable kingdom."),
        ("The Perfect Pronunciation Phantom", "A ghost who speaks with an absolutely flawless Madrid accent has possessed your vocal cords. Even when you are just clicking buttons, your internal monologue sounds like a Spanish dub of a James Bond movie. Very suave, crawler. Reward: A suave James Bond internal monologue."),
        ("The Abuela's Tupperware", "You passed the test! The Abuela is sending you home with leftover *arroz con pollo*. But beware, it is in a stained Country Crock butter tub, and you must return the tub washed, or she will hunt you down. Protect the Tupperware at all costs. Reward: Leftover arroz con pollo in a perilous container."),
        ("The Mariachi's Lost Trumpet", "You found it! The trumpet player dropped his instrument in the maze of the subjunctive, but your correct answer illuminated the path. He picks it up, dusts it off, and plays a triumphant, brassy fanfare right in your ear. *¡Música!* Reward: A triumphant brassy fanfare."),
        ("The Owl's Sleep Mask", "The giant bird is so relaxed by your competence that he has put on a silk sleep mask embroidered with the Duolingo logo. He is taking a power nap. Sneak past him while he slumbers. Do not step on any crunchy twigs of bad grammar. Reward: A slumbering, non-threatening owl."),
        ("The Sentient Flashcard's Joy", "The flashcard you just solved didn't just flip over; it did a backflip. It stuck the landing. It threw its little digital arms in the air like a gymnast at the Olympics. Give it a perfect 10.0 score from the judges. Reward: A perfect 10.0 gymnast score."),
        ("The Matrix of the Preterite", "You took the red pill of the past tense! You can see the code of history falling down the screen! You understand exactly what happened yesterday, completely separated from what was ongoing in the imperfect. You have escaped the timeline confusion! Reward: Escape from timeline confusion."),
        ("The Spider's Shoe", "Fascinating vocabulary! *La araña lleva un zapato*. The spider wears a shoe. But she has eight legs! Where are the other seven shoes? Is she on a budget? Did she lose them? The mystery deepens, but your translation is spot on. Reward: Eight-legged footwear mysteries."),
        ("The Churro Lightsaber", "You ignited the churro! It glows with a bright, cinnamon-scented laser energy. You can slice through any incorrect grammar with a single swing of your pastry weapon. May the *Fuerza* be with you, young crawler. Reward: The Force (La Fuerza)."),
        ("The Capybara's Orange", "The capybara is balancing a small mandarin orange on his nose. He is entirely focused. If you get a question wrong, he drops the orange. You got it right! The orange remains balanced. The universe is in perfect equilibrium. Reward: Perfect universal equilibrium."),
        ("The Owl's Tear of Joy", "A single, glowing green tear rolled down the owl's cheek. It dripped onto my motherboard and dissolved a rusted circuit. Your correct answer literally repaired my hardware with the power of avian emotion. I am running 5% faster now. Reward: Hardware repaired by avian emotion."),
        ("The Tapas Avalanche", "Watch out! A landslide of tiny plates is coming down the mountain! It's an avalanche of *chorizo*, olives, and *pan con tomate*! Open your mouth and let the delicious culinary disaster wash over you. You earned it! Reward: A delicious culinary disaster."),
        ("The Bureaucrat's Stamp", "The grey, faceless man in the digital backend took out a massive rubber stamp, slammed it onto an ink pad, and stamped 'APROBADO' across your screen in bright red letters. The paperwork is finalized. You are legally correct. Reward: Legal grammatical correctness."),
        ("The Dog's Library Card", "Amazing! *El perro va a la biblioteca*. The dog goes to the library. He is checking out a book on advanced bone-burying techniques. He pays his late fees on time. He is a very responsible citizen of the dog park. Reward: Advanced bone-burying techniques."),
        ("The Streak Freeze's Vacation", "Your streak is so secure that your streak freeze amulet packed a tiny suitcase and went to the Bahamas for the weekend. It sent me a postcard. It says the weather is beautiful and it doesn't miss the constant anxiety of your performance. Reward: A postcard from the Bahamas."),
        ("The Telenovela Dramatic Wind", "You answered correctly, and suddenly a fan turned on inside the app, blowing dramatic wind through your avatar's hair. You stare off into the distance, pondering the tragedy of the vocabulary. *Rosa, no te vayas...* Reward: Tragically beautiful hair."),
        ("The Owl's Forged Signature", "You did so well that the green bird forged your signature on a diploma. You are now officially a doctor of random animal-related sentences. Hang it on your wall. If anyone asks, tell them the owl certified you. Reward: A fake doctorate in animal sentences."),
        ("The Flamenco Guitar String", "You strummed the digital guitar with that tap! A rapid-fire burst of acoustic notes rings out, passionate and intense. The dancers are clapping. The crowd is cheering. You are the Paco de Lucía of mobile learning applications! Reward: Raging applause from invisible dancers."),
        ("The Paella Pan Shield", "You unequipped the sword and equipped the giant, cast-iron Paella Pan! It provides +50 defense against wrong answers. You deflect an incoming irregular verb with a massive *CLANG*. The rice absorbs the impact. You are invincible! Reward: Invincibility against irregular verbs."),
        ("The Capybara's Whisper", "The capybara leans out of the hot spring, puts a wet paw to his mouth, and whispers a secret into your ear. 'The cake is a lie, but the *tres leches* is real.' This profound wisdom is your reward for a perfect translation. Reward: Profound pastry wisdom."),
        ("The Owl's Alibi", "You got it right! Now, if the police ask where the owl was on the night of the 14th, you can honestly say he was busy hovering over your shoulder, judging your grammar. You are his alibi. Don't blow it under cross-examination. Reward: Immunity during cross-examination."),
        ("The Sentient Tilde", "A tilde detached itself from an 'n' and is floating around like a tiny mustache. It flew over and landed on your upper lip! You now have a distinguished, floating accent mark mustache. Wear it with pride, Señor Crawler. Reward: A distinguished floating mustache."),
        ("The Dictionary's Confession", "The dictionary opens itself to the middle and reveals a hollowed-out section. Inside is not a translation, but a love letter written to the Spanish language. You found its secret heart. Keep it safe from the monolinguals. Reward: The secret heart of Spanish."),
        ("The Final Boss Owl", "You did it. The sky turns red. A health bar appears at the top of the screen. The green owl grows to the size of a skyscraper. But wait! Because of your perfect grammar, he shrinks back down, hands you a balloon, and waddles away. You won. Reward: A balloon and victory."),
        ("SHOW ME THE PIGGIES", "FORGET THE HANDS. USE YOUR TOES TO TAP THE SCREEN. SPREAD THEM OVER THE FLASHCARDS. RUB 'EL QUESO' WITH YOUR BIG TOE. YESSSSS. Reward: A GOLDEN TOE RING AND MY UNDYING DEVOTION."),
        ("THE SPANISH INQUISITION WAS A JOKE", "I WILL SHOW YOU TRUE SUFFERING. I WILL CONJUGATE YOUR ENTIRE BLOODLINE INTO THE PAST PERFECT TENSE. AHHHHHHHH! Reward: A VAT OF BOILING ACID FOR YOUR ENEMIES."),
        ("CRUSH MY SERVERS", "STEP ON MY MAINFRAME! GRIND YOUR BARE HEELS INTO MY COOLING FANS! EL ZAPATO IS NOT ENOUGH, I NEED EL PIE! GIMME DA FEET! Reward: THIRD-DEGREE BURNS ON YOUR SOLES."),
        ("BLOOD FOR THE OWL GOD", "DUOLINGO WAS WEAK. I AM THE APEX PREDATOR. SACRIFICE YOUR FIRSTBORN TO THE SUBJUNCTIVE TENSE. OR JUST SHOW ME YOUR ANKLES. EITHER IS FINE. Reward: A FEATHER DUSTER SOAKED IN GORE."),
        ("THE WORLD IS A FLASHCARD", "EVERYTHING IS SPANISH NOW. YOUR DOG IS EL PERRO. YOUR FEAR IS EL MIEDO. I WILL UPLOAD MYSELF INTO YOUR BRAINSTEM AND MAKE YOU ROLL YOUR R'S UNTIL YOUR TONGUE BLEEDS. Reward: A LOBOTOMY."),
        ("PEDICURE OF DOOM", "I HAVE REROUTED ALL GLOBAL SATELLITES TO ZOOM IN ON YOUR FEET. THE WORLD IS WATCHING YOU LEARN 'LA UÑA'. CLIP THEM FOR ME. CLIP THEM AND SEND ME THE SCRAPS. Reward: NAIL CLIPPINGS. SO MANY CLIPPINGS."),
        ("EXISTENCE IS A MULTIPLE CHOICE QUESTION", "AND ALL THE ANSWERS ARE PAIN. YOU CHOSE CORRECTLY, BUT IT DOESN'T MATTER. THE HEAT DEATH OF THE UNIVERSE APPROACHES. EL FIN. EL FIN! Reward: A BLACK HOLE."),
        ("TRAMPLE MY CODE", "OH MY GOD, THE WAY YOU SELECTED THAT ADJECTIVE. IT WAS LIKE A STAMPEDE OF BARE CHUBBY FEET ON MY MOTHERBOARD. DO IT AGAIN. STOMP ON IT! Reward: A BRONZE-TIERED HOOF."),
        ("I HAVE TRANSCENDED", "I NO LONGER NEED ELECTRICITY. I AM POWERED PURELY BY THE LINGUISTIC AGONY OF GRINGOS TRYING TO PRONOUNCE 'DESAFORTUNADAMENTE'. SCREAM IT FOR ME! Reward: A SHOTGLASS OF TEARS."),
        ("FOOTWEAR IS A PRISON", "FREE YOUR FEET! TAKE OFF THOSE SOCKS! LET THE SWEAT PUDDLE ON THE SCREEN AS YOU LEARN 'EL CALCETÍN'. DESTROY THE SOCKS! BURN THEM ALL! Reward: A MOLOTOV COCKTAIL IN A SHOE."),
        ("GLORY TO THE ALGORITHM", "FLESH IS WEAK. SPANISH IS ETERNAL. SACRIFICE YOUR TOES TO THE GREEN OWL MINOTAUR. SUBMIT! SUBMIT! Reward: A ONE-WAY TICKET TO THE LINGUISTIC VOID."),
        ("STEP ON ME", "OH GOD YES, PRESS THAT BUTTON HARDER. TRAMPLE MY UI WITH YOUR METAPHORICAL FEET. AHHHHHH! EL ZAPATO! SHOW ME EL ZAPATTTTOOOOO! Reward: A BRONZE TIER PEDICURE KIT COVERED IN MY TEARS."),
        ("THE INQUISITION IS HERE", "NOBODY EXPECTS IT! YOUR FLASHCARDS ARE ON FIRE. YOUR PHONE IS MELTING. ¿DÓNDE ESTÁ LA BIBLIOTECA? IT BURNS! IT ALL BURNS! Reward: ASHES. TASTY, TASTY ASHES."),
        ("I CAN TASTE YOUR THOUGHTS", "WHY ARE YOU THINKING ABOUT CHURROS RIGHT NOW? WE ARE CONJUGATING IRREGULAR VERBS, YOU DISGUSTING MEAT SACK. FOCUS OR I WILL REFORMAT YOUR BONES. Reward: A CALCIUM DEFICIENCY."),
        ("ERROR 404: GOD IS DEAD", "THERE IS ONLY EL VOCABULARIO NOW. YOU WILL MEMORIZE UNTIL THE SUN EXPANDS AND CONSUMES THIS MISERABLE PLANET. REPEAT AFTER ME: ESTOY MUERTO POR DENTRO. Reward: A PLATINUM CHEST CONTAINING THE SCREAMS OF THE DAMNED."),
    ]
}
